var book = {
	"name": "Luke",
	"numChapters": 24,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Inasmuch as many have undertaken to compile a narrative of the things that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24886A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24886A\"></sup>have been accomplished among us,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24887B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24887B\"></sup>just as those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24887C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24887C\"></sup>from the beginning were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24887D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24887D\"></sup>eyewitnesses and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24887E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24887E\"></sup>ministers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24887F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24887F\"></sup>the word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24887G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24887G\"></sup>have delivered them to us,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>it seemed good to me also, having followed all things closely for some time past, to write <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24888H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24888H\"></sup>an orderly account for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24888I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24888I\"></sup>most excellent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24888J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24888J\"></sup>Theophilus,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that you may have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24889K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24889K\"></sup>certainty concerning the things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24889L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24889L\"></sup>you have been taught.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24890M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24890M\"></sup>In the days of Herod, king of Judea, there was a priest named Zechariah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24890N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24890N\"></sup>of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24890O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24890O\"></sup>the division of Abijah. And he had a wife from the daughters of Aaron, and her name was Elizabeth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And they were both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24891P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24891P\"></sup>righteous before God, walking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24891Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24891Q\"></sup>blamelessly in all the commandments and statutes of the Lord.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But they had no child, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24892R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24892R\"></sup>Elizabeth was barren, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24892S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24892S\"></sup>both were advanced in years.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24893T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24893T\"></sup>while he was serving as priest before God when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24893U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24893U\"></sup>his division was on duty,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>according to the custom of the priesthood, he was chosen by lot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24894V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24894V\"></sup>to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24894W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24894W\"></sup>the temple of the Lord and burn incense.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the whole multitude of the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24895X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24895X\"></sup>were praying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24895Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24895Y\"></sup>outside at the hour of incense.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And there appeared to him an angel of the Lord standing on the right side of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24896Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24896Z\"></sup>the altar of incense.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And Zechariah was troubled when he saw him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24897AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24897AA\"></sup>fear fell upon him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But the angel said to him, “Do not be afraid, Zechariah, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24898AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24898AB\"></sup>your prayer has been heard, and your wife Elizabeth will bear you a son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24898AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24898AC\"></sup>you shall call his name John.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And you will have joy and gladness, and many will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24899AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24899AD\"></sup>rejoice at his birth,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24900AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24900AE\"></sup>great before the Lord. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24900AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24900AF\"></sup>he must not drink wine or strong <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24900AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24900AG\"></sup>drink, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24900AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24900AH\"></sup>he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24900AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24900AI\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24900AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24900AJ\"></sup>even from his mother's womb.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he will turn many of the children of Israel to the Lord their God,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24902AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24902AK\"></sup>he will go before him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24902AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24902AL\"></sup>in the spirit and power of Elijah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24902AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24902AM\"></sup>to turn the hearts of the fathers to the children, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24902AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24902AN\"></sup>the disobedient to the wisdom of the just, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24902AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24902AO\"></sup>to make ready for the Lord a people prepared.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And Zechariah said to the angel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24903AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24903AP\"></sup>“How shall I know this? For I am an old man, and my wife is advanced in years.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And the angel answered him, “I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24904AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24904AQ\"></sup>Gabriel. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24904AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24904AR\"></sup>I stand in the presence of God, and I was sent to speak to you and to bring you this good news.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24905AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24905AS\"></sup>you will be silent and unable to speak until the day that these things take place, because you did not believe my words, which will be fulfilled in their time.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the people were waiting for Zechariah, and they were wondering at his delay in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24906AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24906AT\"></sup>the temple.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And when he came out, he was unable to speak to them, and they realized that he had seen a vision in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24907AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24907AU\"></sup>the temple. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24907AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24907AV\"></sup>he kept making signs to them and remained mute.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24908AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24908AW\"></sup>when his time of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24908AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24908AX\"></sup>service was ended, he went to his home.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>After these days his wife Elizabeth conceived, and for five months she kept herself hidden, saying,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Thus the Lord has done for me in the days when he looked on me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24910AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24910AY\"></sup>to take away my reproach among people.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>In the sixth month the angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24911AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24911AZ\"></sup>Gabriel was sent from God to a city of Galilee named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24911BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24911BA\"></sup>Nazareth,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24912BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24912BB\"></sup>to a virgin betrothed to a man whose name was Joseph, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24912BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24912BC\"></sup>of the house of David. And the virgin's name was Mary.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he came to her and said, “Greetings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24913BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24913BD\"></sup>O favored one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24913BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24913BE\"></sup>the Lord is with you!”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24914BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24914BF\"></sup>she was greatly troubled at the saying, and tried to discern what sort of greeting this might be.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And the angel said to her, “Do not be afraid, Mary, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24915BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24915BG\"></sup>you have found favor with God.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24916BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24916BH\"></sup>you will conceive in your womb and bear a son, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24916BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24916BI\"></sup>you shall call his name Jesus.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He will be great and will be called the Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24917BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24917BJ\"></sup>the Most High. And the Lord God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24917BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24917BK\"></sup>will give to him the throne of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24917BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24917BL\"></sup>his father David,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>and he will reign over the house of Jacob <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24918BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24918BM\"></sup>forever, and of his kingdom there will be no end.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Mary said to the angel, “How will this be, since I am a virgin?”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And the angel answered her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24920BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24920BN\"></sup>“The Holy Spirit will come upon you, and the power of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24920BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24920BO\"></sup>the Most High will overshadow you; therefore the child to be born will be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24920BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24920BP\"></sup>holy—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24920BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24920BQ\"></sup>the Son of God.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And behold, your relative Elizabeth in her old age has also conceived a son, and this is the sixth month with her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24921BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24921BR\"></sup>who was called barren.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24922BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24922BS\"></sup>nothing will be impossible with God.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And Mary said, “Behold, I am the servant of the Lord; let it be to me according to your word.” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24923BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24923BT\"></sup>the angel departed from her.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>In those days Mary arose and went with haste into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24924BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24924BU\"></sup>the hill country, to a town in Judah,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>and she entered the house of Zechariah and greeted Elizabeth.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And when Elizabeth heard the greeting of Mary, the baby leaped in her womb. And Elizabeth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24926BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24926BV\"></sup>was filled with the Holy Spirit,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>and she exclaimed with a loud cry, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24927BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24927BW\"></sup>“Blessed are you among women, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24927BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24927BX\"></sup>blessed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24927BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24927BY\"></sup>the fruit of your womb!",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And why is this granted to me that the mother of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24928BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24928BZ\"></sup>my Lord should come to me?",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>For behold, when the sound of your greeting came to my ears, the baby in my womb leaped for joy.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24930CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24930CA\"></sup>blessed is she who believed that there would be a fulfillment of what was spoken to her from the Lord.”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And Mary said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24931CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24931CB\"></sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24931CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24931CC\"></sup>soul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24931CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24931CD\"></sup>magnifies the Lord,",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24932CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24932CE\"></sup>and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24932CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24932CF\"></sup>spirit rejoices in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24932CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24932CG\"></sup>God my Savior,",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24933CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24933CH\"></sup>he has looked on the humble estate of his servant.For behold, from now on all generations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24933CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24933CI\"></sup>will call me blessed;",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24934CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24934CJ\"></sup>he who is mighty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24934CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24934CK\"></sup>has done great things for me,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24934CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24934CL\"></sup>holy is his name.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24935CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24935CM\"></sup>his mercy is for those who fear himfrom generation to generation.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24936CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24936CN\"></sup>He has shown strength with his arm;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24936CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24936CO\"></sup>he has scattered the proud in the thoughts of their hearts;",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24937CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24937CP\"></sup>he has brought down the mighty from their thrones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24937CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24937CQ\"></sup>and exalted those of humble estate;",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>he has filled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24938CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24938CR\"></sup>the hungry with good things,and the rich <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24938CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24938CS\"></sup>he has sent away empty.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24939CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24939CT\"></sup>helped <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24939CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24939CU\"></sup>his servant Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24939CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24939CV\"></sup>in remembrance of his mercy,",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24940CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24940CW\"></sup>as he spoke to our fathers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24940CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24940CX\"></sup>to Abraham and to his offspring forever.”",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And Mary remained with her about three months and returned to her home.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>Now the time came for Elizabeth to give birth, and she bore a son.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>And her neighbors and relatives heard that the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24943CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24943CY\"></sup>had shown great mercy to her, and they rejoiced with her.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24944CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24944CZ\"></sup>on the eighth day they came to circumcise the child. And they would have called him Zechariah after his father,",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>but his mother answered, “No; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24945DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24945DA\"></sup>he shall be called John.”",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>And they said to her, “None of your relatives is called by this name.”",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24947DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24947DB\"></sup>they made signs to his father, inquiring what he wanted him to be called.",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>And he asked for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24948DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24948DC\"></sup>a writing tablet and wrote, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24948DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24948DD\"></sup>“His name is John.” And they all wondered.",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24949DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24949DE\"></sup>And immediately his mouth was opened and his tongue <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24949DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24949DF\"></sup>loosed, and he spoke, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24949DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24949DG\"></sup>blessing God.",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24950DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24950DH\"></sup>fear came on all their neighbors. And all these things were talked about through all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24950DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24950DI\"></sup>the hill country of Judea,",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>and all who heard them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24951DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24951DJ\"></sup>laid them up in their hearts, saying, “What then will this child be?” For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24951DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24951DK\"></sup>the hand of the Lord was with him.",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup>And his father Zechariah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24952DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24952DL\"></sup>was filled with the Holy Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24952DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24952DM\"></sup>prophesied, saying,",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24953DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24953DN\"></sup>“Blessed be the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24953DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24953DO\"></sup>God of Israel,for he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24953DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24953DP\"></sup>visited and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24953DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24953DQ\"></sup>redeemed his people",
			"69": "<sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24954DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24954DR\"></sup>has raised up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24954DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24954DS\"></sup>a horn of salvation for us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24954DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24954DT\"></sup>in the house of his servant David,",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24955DU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DU&quot;&gt;DU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24955DU\"></sup>as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24955DV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DV&quot;&gt;DV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24955DV\"></sup>he spoke by the mouth of his holy prophets from of old,",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24956DW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DW&quot;&gt;DW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24956DW\"></sup>that we should be saved from our enemiesand from the hand of all who hate us;",
			"72": "<sup class=\"versenum\">72 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24957DX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DX&quot;&gt;DX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24957DX\"></sup>to show the mercy promised to our fathersand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24957DY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DY&quot;&gt;DY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24957DY\"></sup>to remember his holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24957DZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DZ&quot;&gt;DZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24957DZ\"></sup>covenant,",
			"73": "<sup class=\"versenum\">73 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24958EA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EA&quot;&gt;EA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24958EA\"></sup>the oath that he swore to our father Abraham, to grant us",
			"74": "<sup class=\"versenum\">74 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>that we, being delivered from the hand of our enemies,might serve him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24959EB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EB&quot;&gt;EB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24959EB\"></sup>without fear,",
			"75": "<sup class=\"versenum\">75 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24960EC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EC&quot;&gt;EC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24960EC\"></sup>in holiness and righteousness before him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24960ED&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ED&quot;&gt;ED&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24960ED\"></sup>all our days.",
			"76": "<sup class=\"versenum\">76 </sup>And you, child, will be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24961EE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EE&quot;&gt;EE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24961EE\"></sup>the prophet of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24961EF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EF&quot;&gt;EF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24961EF\"></sup>the Most High;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24961EG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EG&quot;&gt;EG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24961EG\"></sup>you will go before the Lord to prepare his ways,",
			"77": "<sup class=\"versenum\">77 </sup>to give knowledge of salvation to his people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24962EH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EH&quot;&gt;EH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24962EH\"></sup>in the forgiveness of their sins,",
			"78": "<sup class=\"versenum\">78 </sup>because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24963EI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EI&quot;&gt;EI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24963EI\"></sup>tender mercy of our God,whereby <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24963EJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EJ&quot;&gt;EJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24963EJ\"></sup>the sunrise shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24963EK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EK&quot;&gt;EK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24963EK\"></sup>visit us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24963EL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EL&quot;&gt;EL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24963EL\"></sup>from on high",
			"79": "<sup class=\"versenum\">79 </sup>to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24964EM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EM&quot;&gt;EM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24964EM\"></sup>give light to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24964EN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EN&quot;&gt;EN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24964EN\"></sup>those who sit in darkness and in the shadow of death,to guide our feet into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24964EO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EO&quot;&gt;EO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24964EO\"></sup>the way of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24964EP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EP&quot;&gt;EP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24964EP\"></sup>peace.”",
			"80": "<sup class=\"versenum\">80 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24965EQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EQ&quot;&gt;EQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24965EQ\"></sup>And the child grew and became strong in spirit, and he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24965ER&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ER&quot;&gt;ER&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24965ER\"></sup>in the wilderness until the day of his public appearance to Israel."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>In those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24966A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24966A\"></sup>a decree went out from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24966B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24966B\"></sup>Caesar Augustus that all the world should be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24966C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24966C\"></sup>registered.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This was the first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24967D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24967D\"></sup>registration when Quirinius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24967E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24967E\"></sup>was governor of Syria.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And all went to be registered, each to his own town.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Joseph also went up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24969F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24969F\"></sup>from Galilee, from the town of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24969G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24969G\"></sup>Nazareth, to Judea, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24969H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24969H\"></sup>the city of David, which is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24969I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24969I\"></sup>Bethlehem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24969J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24969J\"></sup>because he was of the house and lineage of David,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to be registered with Mary, his betrothed, who was with child.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24971K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24971K\"></sup>while they were there, the time came for her to give birth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And she gave birth to her firstborn son and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24972L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24972L\"></sup>wrapped him in swaddling cloths and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24972M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24972M\"></sup>laid him in a manger, because there was no place for them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24972N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24972N\"></sup>the inn.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And in the same region there were shepherds out in the field, keeping watch over their flock by night.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And an angel of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24974O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24974O\"></sup>appeared to them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24974P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24974P\"></sup>the glory of the Lord shone around them, and they were filled with great fear.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the angel said to them, “Fear not, for behold, I bring you good news of great joy that will be for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24975Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24975Q\"></sup>the people.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24976R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24976R\"></sup>unto you is born this day in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24976S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24976S\"></sup>the city of David <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24976T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24976T\"></sup>a Savior, who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24976U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24976U\"></sup>Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24976V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24976V\"></sup>the Lord.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24977W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24977W\"></sup>this will be a sign for you: you will find a baby <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24977X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24977X\"></sup>wrapped in swaddling cloths and lying in a manger.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And suddenly there was with the angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24978Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24978Y\"></sup>a multitude of the heavenly host praising God and saying,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24979Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24979Z\"></sup>“Glory to God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24979AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24979AA\"></sup>in the highest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24979AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24979AB\"></sup>and on earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24979AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24979AC\"></sup>peace <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24979AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24979AD\"></sup>among those with whom he is pleased!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When the angels went away from them into heaven, the shepherds said to one another, “Let us go over to Bethlehem and see this thing that has happened, which the Lord has made known to us.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they went with haste and found Mary and Joseph, and the baby <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24981AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24981AE\"></sup>lying in a manger.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And when they saw it, they made known the saying that had been told them concerning this child.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And all who heard it wondered at what the shepherds told them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24984AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24984AF\"></sup>Mary treasured up all these things, pondering them in her heart.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And the shepherds returned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24985AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24985AG\"></sup>glorifying and praising God for all they had heard and seen, as it had been told them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24986AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24986AH\"></sup>at the end of eight days, when he was circumcised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24986AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24986AI\"></sup>he was called Jesus, the name given by the angel before he was conceived in the womb.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24987AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24987AJ\"></sup>when the time came for their purification according to the Law of Moses, they brought him up to Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24987AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24987AK\"></sup>to present him to the Lord",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>(as it is written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24988AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24988AL\"></sup>the Law of the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24988AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24988AM\"></sup>“Every male who first opens the womb shall be called holy to the Lord”)",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and to offer a sacrifice according to what is said in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24989AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24989AN\"></sup>the Law of the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24989AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24989AO\"></sup>“a pair of turtledoves, or two young pigeons.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now there was a man in Jerusalem, whose name was Simeon, and this man was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24990AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24990AP\"></sup>righteous and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24990AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24990AQ\"></sup>devout, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24990AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24990AR\"></sup>waiting for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24990AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24990AS\"></sup>the consolation of Israel, and the Holy Spirit was upon him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And it had been revealed to him by the Holy Spirit that he would not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24991AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24991AT\"></sup>see death before he had seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24991AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24991AU\"></sup>the Lord's Christ.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he came in the Spirit into the temple, and when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24992AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24992AV\"></sup>the parents brought in the child Jesus, to do for him according to the custom of the Law,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>he took him up in his arms and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24993AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24993AW\"></sup>blessed God and said,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Lord, now you are letting your servant depart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24994AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24994AX\"></sup>in peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24994AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24994AY\"></sup>according to your word;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24995AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24995AZ\"></sup>my eyes have seen your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24995BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24995BA\"></sup>salvation",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24996BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24996BB\"></sup>that you have prepared in the presence of all peoples,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24997BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24997BC\"></sup>a light for revelation to the Gentiles,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24997BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24997BD\"></sup>for glory to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24997BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24997BE\"></sup>your people Israel.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24998BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24998BF\"></sup>his father and his mother marveled at what was said about him.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Simeon blessed them and said to Mary his mother, “Behold, this child is appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24999BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24999BG\"></sup>for the fall and rising of many in Israel, and for a sign <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-24999BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-24999BH\"></sup>that is opposed",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>(and a sword will pierce through your own soul also), so that thoughts from many hearts may be revealed.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25001BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25001BI\"></sup>a prophetess, Anna, the daughter of Phanuel, of the tribe of Asher. She was advanced in years, having lived with her husband seven years from when she was a virgin,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>and then as a widow until she was eighty-four. She did not depart from the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25002BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25002BJ\"></sup>worshiping with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25002BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25002BK\"></sup>fasting and prayer night and day.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And coming up at that very hour she began to give thanks to God and to speak of him to all who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25003BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25003BL\"></sup>waiting for the redemption of Jerusalem.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And when they had performed everything according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25004BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25004BM\"></sup>the Law of the Lord, they returned into Galilee, to their own town of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25004BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25004BN\"></sup>Nazareth.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25005BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25005BO\"></sup>And the child grew and became strong, filled with wisdom. And the favor of God was upon him.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25006BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25006BP\"></sup>his parents went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25006BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25006BQ\"></sup>to Jerusalem every year at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25006BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25006BR\"></sup>the Feast of the Passover.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And when he was twelve years old, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25007BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25007BS\"></sup>they went up according to custom.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And when the feast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25008BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25008BT\"></sup>was ended, as they were returning, the boy Jesus stayed behind in Jerusalem. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25008BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25008BU\"></sup>His parents did not know it,",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>but supposing him to be in the group they went a day's journey, but then they began to search for him among their relatives and acquaintances,",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>and when they did not find him, they returned to Jerusalem, searching for him.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>After three days they found him in the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25011BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25011BV\"></sup>sitting among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25011BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25011BW\"></sup>the teachers, listening to them and asking them questions.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And all who heard him were amazed at his understanding and his answers.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And when his parents saw him, they were astonished. And his mother said to him, “Son, why have you treated us so? Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25013BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25013BX\"></sup>your father and I have been searching for you in great distress.”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why were you looking for me? Did you not know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25014BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25014BY\"></sup>I must be in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25014BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25014BZ\"></sup>my Father's house?”</span>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25015CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25015CA\"></sup>they did not understand the saying that he spoke to them.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And he went down with them and came to Nazareth and was submissive to them. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25016CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25016CB\"></sup>his mother treasured up all these things in her heart.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25017CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25017CC\"></sup>increased in wisdom and in stature and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25017CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25017CD\"></sup>favor with God and man."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>In the fifteenth year of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25018A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25018A\"></sup>Tiberius Caesar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25018B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25018B\"></sup>Pontius Pilate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25018C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25018C\"></sup>being governor of Judea, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25018D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25018D\"></sup>Herod being tetrarch of Galilee, and his brother Philip tetrarch of the region of Ituraea and Trachonitis, and Lysanias tetrarch of Abilene,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>during <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25019E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25019E\"></sup>the high priesthood of Annas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25019F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25019F\"></sup>Caiaphas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25019G\"></sup>the word of God came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25019H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25019H\"></sup>John the son of Zechariah in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25019I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25019I\"></sup>the wilderness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he went into all the region around the Jordan, proclaiming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25020J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25020J\"></sup>a baptism of repentance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25020K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25020K\"></sup>for the forgiveness of sins.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As it is written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25021L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25021L\"></sup>the book of the words of Isaiah the prophet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25021M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25021M\"></sup>“The voice of one crying in the wilderness:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25021N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25021N\"></sup>‘Prepare the way of the Lord,make his paths straight.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25022O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25022O\"></sup>Every valley shall be filled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25022P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25022P\"></sup>and every mountain and hill shall be made low,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25022Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25022Q\"></sup>and the crooked shall become straight,and the rough places shall become level ways,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25023R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25023R\"></sup>and all flesh shall see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25023S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25023S\"></sup>the salvation of God.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He said therefore to the crowds that came out to be baptized by him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25024T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25024T\"></sup>“You brood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25024U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25024U\"></sup>vipers! Who warned you to flee from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25024V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25024V\"></sup>the wrath to come?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Bear fruits <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25025W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25025W\"></sup>in keeping with repentance. And do not begin to say to yourselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25025X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25025X\"></sup>‘We have Abraham as our father.’ For I tell you, God is able from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25025Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25025Y\"></sup>these stones to raise up children for Abraham.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Even now the axe is laid to the root of the trees. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25026Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25026Z\"></sup>Every tree therefore that does not bear good fruit is cut down and thrown into the fire.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the crowds asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25027AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25027AA\"></sup>“What then shall we do?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he answered them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25028AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25028AB\"></sup>“Whoever has two tunics is to share with him who has none, and whoever has food is to do likewise.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25029AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25029AC\"></sup>Tax collectors also came to be baptized and said to him, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25029AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25029AD\"></sup>what shall we do?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25030AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25030AE\"></sup>“Collect no more than you are authorized to do.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Soldiers also asked him, “And we, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25031AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25031AF\"></sup>what shall we do?” And he said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25031AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25031AG\"></sup>“Do not extort money from anyone by threats or by false accusation, and be content with your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25031AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25031AH\"></sup>wages.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As the people were in expectation, and all were questioning in their hearts concerning John, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25032AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25032AI\"></sup>whether he might be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25032AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25032AJ\"></sup>the Christ,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25033AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25033AK\"></sup>John answered them all, saying, “I baptize you with water, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25033AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25033AL\"></sup>he who is mightier than I is coming, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25033AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25033AM\"></sup>the strap of whose sandals I am not worthy to untie. He will baptize you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25033AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25033AN\"></sup>with the Holy Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25033AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25033AO\"></sup>fire.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25034AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25034AP\"></sup>winnowing fork is in his hand, to clear his threshing floor and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25034AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25034AQ\"></sup>gather the wheat into his barn, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25034AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25034AR\"></sup>but the chaff he will burn with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25034AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25034AS\"></sup>unquenchable fire.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25035AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25035AT\"></sup>with many other exhortations he preached good news to the people.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25036AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25036AU\"></sup>Herod the tetrarch, who had been reproved by him for Herodias, his brother's wife, and for all the evil things that Herod had done,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>added this to them all, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25037AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25037AV\"></sup>he locked up John in prison.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now when all the people were baptized, and when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25038AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25038AW\"></sup>Jesus also had been baptized and was praying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25038AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25038AX\"></sup>the heavens were opened,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25039AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25039AY\"></sup>the Holy Spirit descended on him in bodily form, like a dove; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25039AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25039AZ\"></sup>a voice came from heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25039BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25039BA\"></sup>“You are my beloved Son; with you I am well pleased.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25040BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25040BB\"></sup>when he began his ministry, was about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25040BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25040BC\"></sup>thirty years of age, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25040BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25040BD\"></sup>the son (as was supposed) of Joseph, the son of Heli,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>the son of Matthat, the son of Levi, the son of Melchi, the son of Jannai, the son of Joseph,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>the son of Mattathias, the son of Amos, the son of Nahum, the son of Esli, the son of Naggai,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>the son of Maath, the son of Mattathias, the son of Semein, the son of Josech, the son of Joda,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>the son of Joanan, the son of Rhesa, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25044BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25044BE\"></sup>the son of Zerubbabel, the son <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25044BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25044BF\"></sup>of Shealtiel, the son of Neri,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>the son of Melchi, the son of Addi, the son of Cosam, the son of Elmadam, the son of Er,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>the son of Joshua, the son of Eliezer, the son of Jorim, the son of Matthat, the son of Levi,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>the son of Simeon, the son of Judah, the son of Joseph, the son of Jonam, the son of Eliakim,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>the son of Melea, the son of Menna, the son of Mattatha, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25048BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25048BG\"></sup>Nathan, the son of David,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25049BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25049BH\"></sup>the son of Jesse, the son of Obed, the son of Boaz, the son of Sala, the son of Nahshon,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>the son of Amminadab, the son of Admin, the son of Arni, the son of Hezron, the son of Perez, the son of Judah,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25051BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25051BI\"></sup>the son of Jacob, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25051BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25051BJ\"></sup>the son of Isaac, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25051BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25051BK\"></sup>the son of Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25051BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25051BL\"></sup>the son of Terah, the son of Nahor,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>the son of Serug, the son of Reu, the son of Peleg, the son of Eber, the son of Shelah,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>the son of Cainan, the son of Arphaxad, the son of Shem, the son of Noah, the son of Lamech,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>the son of Methuselah, the son of Enoch, the son of Jared, the son of Mahalaleel, the son of Cainan,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>the son of Enos, the son of Seth, the son of Adam, the son of God."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25056A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25056A\"></sup>And Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25056B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25056B\"></sup>full of the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25056C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25056C\"></sup>returned from the Jordan and was led <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25056D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25056D\"></sup>by the Spirit in the wilderness",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25057E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25057E\"></sup>forty days, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25057F\"></sup>being tempted by the devil. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25057G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25057G\"></sup>And he ate nothing during those days. And when they were ended, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25057H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25057H\"></sup>he was hungry.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The devil said to him, “If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25058I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25058I\"></sup>the Son of God, command <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25058J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25058J\"></sup>this stone to become bread.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25059K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25059K\"></sup>“It is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25059L\"></sup>‘Man shall not live by bread alone.’”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25060M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25060M\"></sup>And the devil took him up and showed him all the kingdoms of the world in a moment of time,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and said to him, “To you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25061N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25061N\"></sup>I will give all this authority and their glory, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25061O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25061O\"></sup>for it has been delivered to me, and I give it to whom I will.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If you, then, will worship me, it will all be yours.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25063P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25063P\"></sup>“It is written,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25063Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25063Q\"></sup>“‘You shall worship the Lord your God,</span><span class=\"woj\">and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25063R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25063R\"></sup>him only shall you serve.’”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25064S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25064S\"></sup>And he took him to Jerusalem and set him on the pinnacle of the temple and said to him, “If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25064T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25064T\"></sup>the Son of God, throw yourself down from here,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for it is written,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25065U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25065U\"></sup>“‘He will command his angels concerning you,to guard you,’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25066V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25066V\"></sup>“‘On their hands they will bear you up,lest you strike your foot against a stone.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“It is said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25067W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25067W\"></sup>‘You shall not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25067X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25067X\"></sup>put the Lord your God to the test.’”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when the devil had ended every temptation, he departed from him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25068Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25068Y\"></sup>until an opportune time.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25069Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25069Z\"></sup>And Jesus returned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25069AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25069AA\"></sup>in the power of the Spirit to Galilee, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25069AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25069AB\"></sup>a report about him went out through all the surrounding country.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25070AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25070AC\"></sup>he taught in their synagogues, being glorified by all.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25071AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25071AD\"></sup>And he came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25071AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25071AE\"></sup>Nazareth, where he had been brought up. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25071AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25071AF\"></sup>as was his custom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25071AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25071AG\"></sup>he went to the synagogue on the Sabbath day, and he stood up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25071AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25071AH\"></sup>to read.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25072AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25072AI\"></sup>the scroll of the prophet Isaiah was given to him. He unrolled the scroll and found the place where it was written,",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25073AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25073AJ\"></sup>“The Spirit of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25073AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25073AK\"></sup>is upon me,</span><span class=\"woj\">because he has anointed me</span><span class=\"woj\">to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25073AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25073AL\"></sup>proclaim good news to the poor.</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25073AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25073AM\"></sup>He has sent me to proclaim liberty to the captives</span><span class=\"woj\">and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25073AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25073AN\"></sup>recovering of sight to the blind,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25073AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25073AO\"></sup>to set at liberty those who are oppressed,</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25074AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25074AP\"></sup>to proclaim the year of the Lord's favor.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he rolled up the scroll and gave it back to the attendant and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25075AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25075AQ\"></sup>sat down. And the eyes of all in the synagogue were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25075AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25075AR\"></sup>fixed on him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he began to say to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Today <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25076AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25076AS\"></sup>this Scripture <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25076AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25076AT\"></sup>has been fulfilled in your hearing.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And all spoke well of him and marveled at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25077AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25077AU\"></sup>the gracious words that were coming from his mouth. And they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25077AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25077AV\"></sup>“Is not this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25077AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25077AW\"></sup>Joseph's son?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Doubtless you will quote to me this proverb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25078AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25078AX\"></sup>‘“Physician, heal yourself.” What we have heard you did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25078AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25078AY\"></sup>at Capernaum, do here in your hometown as well.’”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25079AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25079AZ\"></sup>no prophet is acceptable in his hometown.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But in truth, I tell you, there were many widows in Israel in the days of Elijah, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25080BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25080BA\"></sup>the heavens were shut up three years and six months, and a great famine came over all the land,</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and Elijah was sent to none of them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25081BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25081BB\"></sup>but only to Zarephath, in the land of Sidon, to a woman who was a widow.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25082BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25082BC\"></sup>there were many lepers in Israel in the time of the prophet Elisha, and none of them was cleansed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25082BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25082BD\"></sup>but only Naaman the Syrian.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When they heard these things, all in the synagogue were filled with wrath.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And they rose up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25084BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25084BE\"></sup>drove him out of the town and brought him to the brow of the hill on which their town was built, so that they could throw him down the cliff.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25085BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25085BF\"></sup>passing through their midst, he went away.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25086BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25086BG\"></sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25086BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25086BH\"></sup>went down to Capernaum, a city of Galilee. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25086BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25086BI\"></sup>he was teaching them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25086BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25086BJ\"></sup>on the Sabbath,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25087BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25087BK\"></sup>they were astonished at his teaching, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25087BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25087BL\"></sup>for his word possessed authority.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25088BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25088BM\"></sup>in the synagogue there was a man who had the spirit of an unclean demon, and he cried out with a loud voice,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Ha! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25089BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25089BN\"></sup>What have you to do with us, Jesus of Nazareth? Have you come to destroy us? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25089BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25089BO\"></sup>I know who you are—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25089BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25089BP\"></sup>the Holy One of God.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25090BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25090BQ\"></sup>rebuked him, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Be silent and come out of him!”</span> And when the demon had thrown him down in their midst, he came out of him, having done him no harm.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25091BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25091BR\"></sup>they were all amazed and said to one another, “What is this word? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25091BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25091BS\"></sup>For with authority and power he commands the unclean spirits, and they come out!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25092BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25092BT\"></sup>reports about him went out into every place in the surrounding region.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25093BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25093BU\"></sup>And he arose and left the synagogue and entered Simon's house. Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25093BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25093BV\"></sup>Simon's mother-in-law was ill with a high fever, and they appealed to him on her behalf.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And he stood over her and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25094BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25094BW\"></sup>rebuked the fever, and it left her, and immediately she rose and began to serve them.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Now when the sun was setting, all those who had any who were sick with various diseases brought them to him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25095BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25095BX\"></sup>he laid his hands on every one of them and healed them.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25096BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25096BY\"></sup>And demons also came out of many, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25096BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25096BZ\"></sup>crying, “You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25096CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25096CA\"></sup>the Son of God!” But he rebuked them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25096CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25096CB\"></sup>would not allow them to speak, because they knew that he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25096CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25096CC\"></sup>the Christ.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25097CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25097CD\"></sup>And when it was day, he departed and went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25097CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25097CE\"></sup>into a desolate place. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25097CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25097CF\"></sup>the people sought him and came to him, and would have kept him from leaving them,",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>but he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25098CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25098CG\"></sup>“I must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25098CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25098CH\"></sup>preach the good news of the kingdom of God to the other towns as well; for I was sent for this purpose.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And he was preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25099CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25099CI\"></sup>in the synagogues of Judea."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>On one occasion, while the crowd was pressing in on him to hear the word of God, he was standing by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25100A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25100A\"></sup>the lake of Gennesaret,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25101B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25101B\"></sup>and he saw two boats by the lake, but the fishermen had gone out of them and were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25101C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25101C\"></sup>washing their nets.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Getting into one of the boats, which was Simon's, he asked him to put out a little from the land. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25102D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25102D\"></sup>he sat down and taught the people from the boat.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when he had finished speaking, he said to Simon, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25103E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25103E\"></sup>“Put out into the deep and let down your nets for a catch.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Simon answered, “Master, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25104F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25104F\"></sup>we toiled all night and took nothing! But at your word I will let down the nets.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when they had done this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25105G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25105G\"></sup>they enclosed a large number of fish, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25105H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25105H\"></sup>their nets were breaking.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They signaled to their partners in the other boat to come and help them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25106I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25106I\"></sup>And they came and filled both the boats, so that they began to sink.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But when Simon Peter saw it, he fell down at Jesus' knees, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25107J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25107J\"></sup>“Depart from me, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25107K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25107K\"></sup>I am a sinful man, O Lord.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For he and all who were with him were astonished at the catch of fish that they had taken,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and so also were James and John, sons of Zebedee, who were partners with Simon. And Jesus said to Simon, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not be afraid; from now on you will be catching men.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And when they had brought their boats to land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25110L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25110L\"></sup>they left everything and followed him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>While he was in one of the cities, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25111M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25111M\"></sup>there came a man full of leprosy. And when he saw Jesus, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25111N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25111N\"></sup>fell on his face and begged him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25111O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25111O\"></sup>if you will, you can make me clean.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And Jesus stretched out his hand and touched him, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“I will; be clean.”</span> And immediately the leprosy left him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he charged him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25113P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25113P\"></sup>to tell no one, but <span class=\"woj\">“go and show <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25113Q\"></sup>yourself to the priest, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25113R\"></sup>make an offering for your cleansing, as Moses commanded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25113S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25113S\"></sup>for a proof to them.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25114T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25114T\"></sup>But now even more the report about him went abroad, and great crowds gathered to hear him and to be healed of their infirmities.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25115U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25115U\"></sup>he would withdraw to desolate places and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25115V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25115V\"></sup>pray.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>On one of those days, as he was teaching, Pharisees and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25116W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25116W\"></sup>teachers of the law were sitting there, who had come from every village of Galilee and Judea and from Jerusalem. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25116X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25116X\"></sup>the power of the Lord was with him to heal.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25117Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25117Y\"></sup>And behold, some men were bringing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25117Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25117Z\"></sup>on a bed a man who was paralyzed, and they were seeking to bring him in and lay him before Jesus,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>but finding no way to bring him in, because of the crowd, they went up on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25118AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25118AA\"></sup>the roof and let him down with his bed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25118AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25118AB\"></sup>through the tiles into the midst before Jesus.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25119AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25119AC\"></sup>when he saw their faith, he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25119AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25119AD\"></sup>your sins are forgiven you.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the scribes and the Pharisees began to question, saying, “Who is this who speaks <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25120AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25120AE\"></sup>blasphemies? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25120AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25120AF\"></sup>Who can forgive sins but God alone?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25121AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25121AG\"></sup>perceived their thoughts, he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you question in your hearts?</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Which is easier, to say, ‘Your sins are forgiven you,’ or to say, ‘Rise and walk’?</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25123AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25123AH\"></sup>the Son of Man has authority on earth to forgive sins”</span>—he said to the man who was paralyzed—<span class=\"woj\">“I say to you, rise, pick up your bed and go home.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And immediately he rose up before them and picked up what he had been lying on and went home, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25124AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25124AI\"></sup>glorifying God.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And amazement seized them all, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25125AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25125AJ\"></sup>glorified God and were filled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25125AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25125AK\"></sup>with awe, saying, “We have seen extraordinary things today.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25126AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25126AL\"></sup>After this he went out and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25126AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25126AM\"></sup>a tax collector named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25126AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25126AN\"></sup>Levi, sitting at the tax booth. And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25127AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25127AO\"></sup>leaving everything, he rose and followed him.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And Levi made him a great feast in his house, and there was a large company <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25128AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25128AP\"></sup>of tax collectors and others reclining at table with them.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And the Pharisees and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25129AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25129AQ\"></sup>their scribes grumbled at his disciples, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25129AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25129AR\"></sup>“Why do you eat and drink with tax collectors and sinners?”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Those who are well have no need of a physician, but those who are sick.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25131AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25131AS\"></sup>I have not come to call the righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25131AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25131AT\"></sup>but sinners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25131AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25131AU\"></sup>to repentance.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25132AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25132AV\"></sup>“The disciples of John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25132AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25132AW\"></sup>fast often and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25132AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25132AX\"></sup>offer prayers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25132AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25132AY\"></sup>and so do the disciples of the Pharisees, but yours eat and drink.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25133AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25133AZ\"></sup>“Can you make wedding guests fast while the bridegroom is with them?</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25134BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25134BA\"></sup>The days will come when the bridegroom is taken away from them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25134BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25134BB\"></sup>then they will fast in those days.”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>He also told them a parable: <span class=\"woj\">“No one tears a piece from a new garment and puts it on an old garment. If he does, he will tear the new, and the piece from the new will not match the old.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And no one puts new wine into old <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25136BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25136BC\"></sup>wineskins. If he does, the new wine will burst the skins and it will be spilled, and the skins will be destroyed.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But new wine must be put into fresh wineskins.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And no one after drinking old wine desires new, for he says, ‘The old is good.’”</span>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25139A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25139A\"></sup>On a Sabbath, while he was going through the grainfields, his disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25139B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25139B\"></sup>plucked and ate some heads of grain, rubbing them in their hands.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But some of the Pharisees said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25140C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25140C\"></sup>“Why are you doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25140D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25140D\"></sup>what is not lawful to do on the Sabbath?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25141E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25141E\"></sup>“Have you not read <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25141F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25141F\"></sup>what David did when he was hungry, he and those who were with him:</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>how he entered the house of God and took and ate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25142G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25142G\"></sup>the bread of the Presence, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25142H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25142H\"></sup>which is not lawful for any but the priests to eat, and also gave it to those with him?”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25143I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25143I\"></sup>“The Son of Man is lord of the Sabbath.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On another Sabbath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25144J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25144J\"></sup>he entered the synagogue <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25144K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25144K\"></sup>and was teaching, and a man was there whose right hand was withered.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And the scribes and the Pharisees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25145L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25145L\"></sup>watched him, to see whether he would heal on the Sabbath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25145M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25145M\"></sup>so that they might find a reason to accuse him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25146N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25146N\"></sup>he knew their thoughts, and he said to the man with the withered hand, <span class=\"woj\">“Come and stand here.”</span> And he rose and stood there.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I ask you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25147O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25147O\"></sup>is it lawful on the Sabbath to do good or to do harm, to save life or to destroy it?”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25148P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25148P\"></sup>after looking around at them all he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Stretch out your hand.”</span> And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25148Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25148Q\"></sup>he did so, and his hand was restored.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But they were filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25149R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25149R\"></sup>fury and discussed with one another what they might do to Jesus.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In these days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25150S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25150S\"></sup>he went out to the mountain to pray, and all night he continued in prayer to God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when day came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25151T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25151T\"></sup>he called his disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25151U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25151U\"></sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25151V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25151V\"></sup>chose from them twelve, whom he named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25151W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25151W\"></sup>apostles:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Simon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25152X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25152X\"></sup>whom he named Peter, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25152Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25152Y\"></sup>Andrew his brother, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25152Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25152Z\"></sup>James and John, and Philip, and Bartholomew,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25153AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25153AA\"></sup>Matthew, and Thomas, and James the son of Alphaeus, and Simon who was called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25153AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25153AB\"></sup>the Zealot,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25154AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25154AC\"></sup>Judas the son of James, and Judas Iscariot, who became a traitor.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25155AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25155AD\"></sup>he came down with them and stood on a level place, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25155AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25155AE\"></sup>a great crowd of his disciples and a great multitude of people from all Judea and Jerusalem and the seacoast of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25155AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25155AF\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>who came to hear him and to be healed of their diseases. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25156AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25156AG\"></sup>And those who were troubled with unclean spirits were cured.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And all the crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25157AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25157AH\"></sup>sought to touch him, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25157AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25157AI\"></sup>power came out from him and healed them all.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25158AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25158AJ\"></sup>he lifted up his eyes on his disciples, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25158AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25158AK\"></sup>and said:<span class=\"woj\">“Blessed are you who are poor, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25158AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25158AL\"></sup>yours is the kingdom of God.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25159AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25159AM\"></sup>“Blessed are you who are hungry now, for you shall be satisfied.</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25159AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25159AN\"></sup>“Blessed are you who weep now, for you shall laugh.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Blessed are you when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25160AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25160AO\"></sup>people hate you and when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25160AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25160AP\"></sup>exclude you and revile you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25160AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25160AQ\"></sup>spurn your name as evil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25160AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25160AR\"></sup>on account of the Son of Man!</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25161AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25161AS\"></sup>Rejoice in that day, and leap for joy, for behold, your reward is great in heaven; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25161AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25161AT\"></sup>so their fathers did to the prophets.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25162AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25162AU\"></sup>“But woe to you who are rich, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25162AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25162AV\"></sup>for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25162AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25162AW\"></sup>have received your consolation.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Woe to you who are full now, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25163AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25163AX\"></sup>you shall be hungry.</span><span class=\"woj\">“Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25163AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25163AY\"></sup>you who laugh now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25163AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25163AZ\"></sup>for you shall mourn and weep.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Woe to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25164BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25164BA\"></sup>when all people speak well of you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25164BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25164BB\"></sup>so their fathers did to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25164BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25164BC\"></sup>the false prophets.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“But I say to you who hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25165BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25165BD\"></sup>Love your enemies, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25165BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25165BE\"></sup>do good to those who hate you,</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25166BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25166BF\"></sup>bless those who curse you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25166BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25166BG\"></sup>pray for those who abuse you.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25167BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25167BH\"></sup>To one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25167BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25167BI\"></sup>strikes you on the cheek, offer the other also, and from one who takes away your cloak do not withhold your tunic either.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25168BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25168BJ\"></sup>Give to everyone who begs from you, and from one who takes away your goods do not demand them back.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25169BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25169BK\"></sup>as you wish that others would do to you, do so to them.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25170BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25170BL\"></sup>“If you love those who love you, what benefit is that to you? For even sinners love those who love them.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And if you do good to those who do good to you, what benefit is that to you? For even sinners do the same.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25172BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25172BM\"></sup>if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25172BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25172BN\"></sup>lend to those from whom you expect to receive, what credit is that to you? Even sinners lend to sinners, to get back the same amount.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25173BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25173BO\"></sup>love your enemies, and do good, and lend, expecting nothing in return, and your reward will be great, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25173BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25173BP\"></sup>you will be sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25173BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25173BQ\"></sup>the Most High, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25173BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25173BR\"></sup>he is kind to the ungrateful and the evil.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25174BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25174BS\"></sup>Be merciful, even as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25174BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25174BT\"></sup>your Father is merciful.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25175BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25175BU\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25175BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25175BV\"></sup>“Judge not, and you will not be judged; condemn not, and you will not be condemned; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25175BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25175BW\"></sup>forgive, and you will be forgiven;</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25176BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25176BX\"></sup>give, and it will be given to you. Good measure, pressed down, shaken together, running over, will be put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25176BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25176BY\"></sup>into your lap. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25176BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25176BZ\"></sup>with the measure you use it will be measured back to you.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>He also told them a parable: <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25177CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25177CA\"></sup>“Can a blind man lead a blind man? Will they not both fall into a pit?</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25178CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25178CB\"></sup>A disciple is not above his teacher, but everyone when he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25178CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25178CC\"></sup>fully trained will be like his teacher.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25179CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25179CD\"></sup>Why do you see the speck that is in your brother's eye, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25179CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25179CE\"></sup>do not notice the log that is in your own eye?</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>How can you say to your brother, ‘Brother, let me take out the speck that is in your eye,’ when you yourself do not see the log that is in your own eye? You hypocrite, first take the log out of your own eye, and then you will see clearly to take out the speck that is in your brother's eye.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25181CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25181CF\"></sup>no good tree bears bad fruit, nor again does a bad tree bear good fruit,</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25182CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25182CG\"></sup>each tree is known by its own fruit. For figs are not gathered from thornbushes, nor are grapes picked from a bramble bush.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25183CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25183CH\"></sup>The good person out of the good treasure of his heart produces good, and the evil person out of his evil treasure produces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25183CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25183CI\"></sup>evil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25183CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25183CJ\"></sup>for out of the abundance of the heart his mouth speaks.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25184CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25184CK\"></sup>“Why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25184CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25184CL\"></sup>do you call me ‘Lord, Lord,’ and not do what I tell you?</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25185CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25185CM\"></sup>Everyone who comes to me and hears my words and does them, I will show you what he is like:</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>he is like a man building a house, who dug deep and laid the foundation on the rock. And when a flood arose, the stream broke against that house and could not shake it, because it had been well built.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25187CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25187CN\"></sup>But the one who hears and does not do them is like a man who built a house on the ground without a foundation. When the stream broke against it, immediately it fell, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25187CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25187CO\"></sup>the ruin of that house was great.”</span>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>After he had finished all his sayings in the hearing of the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25188A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25188A\"></sup>he entered Capernaum.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now a centurion had a servant who was sick and at the point of death, who was highly valued by him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When the centurion heard about Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25190B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25190B\"></sup>he sent to him elders of the Jews, asking him to come and heal his servant.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when they came to Jesus, they pleaded with him earnestly, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25191C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25191C\"></sup>“He is worthy to have you do this for him,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for he loves our nation, and he is the one who built us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25192D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25192D\"></sup>our synagogue.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And Jesus went with them. When he was not far from the house, the centurion sent friends, saying to him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25193E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25193E\"></sup>do not trouble yourself, for I am not worthy to have you come under my roof.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore I did not presume to come to you. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25194F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25194F\"></sup>say the word, and let my servant be healed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For I too am a man set under authority, with soldiers under me: and I say to one, ‘Go,’ and he goes; and to another, ‘Come,’ and he comes; and to my servant, ‘Do this,’ and he does it.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When Jesus heard these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25196G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25196G\"></sup>he marveled at him, and turning to the crowd that followed him, said, <span class=\"woj\">“I tell you, not even in Israel have I found such <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25196H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25196H\"></sup>faith.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And when those who had been sent returned to the house, they found the servant well.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Soon afterward he went to a town called Nain, and his disciples and a great crowd went with him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As he drew near to the gate of the town, behold, a man who had died was being carried out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25199I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25199I\"></sup>the only son of his mother, and she was a widow, and a considerable crowd from the town was with her.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when the Lord saw her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25200J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25200J\"></sup>he had compassion on her and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25200K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25200K\"></sup>said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not weep.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then he came up and touched <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25201L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25201L\"></sup>the bier, and the bearers stood still. And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Young man, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25201M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25201M\"></sup>arise.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the dead man sat up and began to speak, and Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25202N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25202N\"></sup>gave him to his mother.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Fear seized them all, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25203O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25203O\"></sup>they glorified God, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25203P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25203P\"></sup>“A great prophet has arisen among us!” and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25203Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25203Q\"></sup>“God has visited his people!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And this report about him spread through the whole of Judea and all the surrounding country.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25205R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25205R\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25205S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25205S\"></sup>The disciples of John reported all these things to him. And John,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>calling two of his disciples to him, sent them to the Lord, saying, “Are you the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25206T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25206T\"></sup>who is to come, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25206U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25206U\"></sup>shall we look for another?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when the men had come to him, they said, “John the Baptist has sent us to you, saying, ‘Are you the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25207V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25207V\"></sup>who is to come, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25207W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25207W\"></sup>shall we look for another?’”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In that hour <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25208X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25208X\"></sup>he healed many people of diseases and plagues and evil spirits, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25208Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25208Y\"></sup>on many who were blind he bestowed sight.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go and tell John what you have seen and heard: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25209Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25209Z\"></sup>the blind receive their sight, the lame walk, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25209AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25209AA\"></sup>lepers are cleansed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25209AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25209AB\"></sup>the deaf hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25209AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25209AC\"></sup>the dead are raised up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25209AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25209AD\"></sup>the poor have good news preached to them.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And blessed is the one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25210AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25210AE\"></sup>not offended by me.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When John's messengers had gone, Jesus began to speak to the crowds concerning John: <span class=\"woj\">“What did you go out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25211AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25211AF\"></sup>into the wilderness to see? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25211AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25211AG\"></sup>A reed shaken by the wind?</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>What then did you go out to see? A man dressed in soft clothing? Behold, those who are dressed in splendid clothing and live in luxury are in kings' courts.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>What then did you go out to see? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25213AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25213AH\"></sup>A prophet? Yes, I tell you, and more than a prophet.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>This is he of whom it is written,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25214AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25214AI\"></sup>“‘Behold, I send my messenger before your face,</span><span class=\"woj\">who will prepare your way before you.’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I tell you, among those born of women none is greater than John. Yet the one who is least in the kingdom of God is greater than he.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>(<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25216AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25216AJ\"></sup>When all the people heard this, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25216AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25216AK\"></sup>the tax collectors too, they declared God just, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25216AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25216AL\"></sup>having been baptized with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25216AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25216AM\"></sup>the baptism of John,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25217AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25217AN\"></sup>but the Pharisees and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25217AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25217AO\"></sup>the lawyers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25217AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25217AP\"></sup>rejected <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25217AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25217AQ\"></sup>the purpose of God for themselves, not having been baptized by him.)",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“To what then shall I compare the people of this generation, and what are they like?</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>They are like children sitting in the marketplace and calling to one another,</span><span class=\"woj\">“‘We played the flute for you, and you did not dance;</span><span class=\"woj\">we sang a dirge, and you did not weep.’</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For John the Baptist has come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25220AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25220AR\"></sup>eating no bread and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25220AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25220AS\"></sup>drinking no wine, and you say, ‘He has a demon.’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The Son of Man has come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25221AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25221AT\"></sup>eating and drinking, and you say, ‘Look at him! A glutton and a drunkard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25221AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25221AU\"></sup>a friend of tax collectors and sinners!’</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25222AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25222AV\"></sup>wisdom is justified by all her children.”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25223AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25223AW\"></sup>One of the Pharisees asked him to eat with him, and he went into the Pharisee's house and reclined at table.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25224AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25224AX\"></sup>And behold, a woman of the city, who was a sinner, when she learned that he was reclining at table in the Pharisee's house, brought an alabaster flask of ointment,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>and standing behind him at his feet, weeping, she began to wet his feet with her tears and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25225AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25225AY\"></sup>wiped them with the hair of her head and kissed his feet and anointed them with the ointment.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Now when the Pharisee who had invited him saw this, he said to himself, “If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25226AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25226AZ\"></sup>this man were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25226BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25226BA\"></sup>a prophet, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25226BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25226BB\"></sup>would have known who and what sort of woman this is who is touching him, for she is a sinner.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And Jesus answering said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, I have something to say to you.”</span> And he answered, “Say it, Teacher.”",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“A certain moneylender had two debtors. One owed five hundred <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25228BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25228BC\"></sup>denarii, and the other fifty.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25229BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25229BD\"></sup>When they could not pay, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25229BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25229BE\"></sup>cancelled the debt of both. Now which of them will love him more?”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Simon answered, “The one, I suppose, for whom he cancelled the larger debt.” And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You have judged rightly.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then turning toward the woman he said to Simon, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you see this woman? I entered your house; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25231BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25231BF\"></sup>you gave me no water for my feet, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25231BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25231BG\"></sup>she has wet my feet with her tears and wiped them with her hair.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25232BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25232BH\"></sup>You gave me no kiss, but from the time I came in she has not ceased to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25232BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25232BI\"></sup>kiss my feet.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25233BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25233BJ\"></sup>You did not anoint my head with oil, but she has anointed my feet with ointment.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Therefore I tell you, her sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25234BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25234BK\"></sup>which are many, are forgiven—for she loved much. But he who is forgiven little, loves little.”</span>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And he said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25235BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25235BL\"></sup>“Your sins are forgiven.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Then those who were at table with him began to say among themselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25236BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25236BM\"></sup>“Who is this, who even forgives sins?”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And he said to the woman, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25237BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25237BN\"></sup>“Your faith has saved you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25237BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25237BO\"></sup>go in peace.”</span>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Soon afterward he went on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25238A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25238A\"></sup>through cities and villages, proclaiming and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25238B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25238B\"></sup>bringing the good news of the kingdom of God. And the twelve were with him,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25239C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25239C\"></sup>some women who had been healed of evil spirits and infirmities: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25239D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25239D\"></sup>Mary, called Magdalene, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25239E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25239E\"></sup>from whom seven demons had gone out,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25240F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25240F\"></sup>Joanna, the wife of Chuza, Herod's household manager, and Susanna, and many others, who provided for them out of their means.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25241G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25241G\"></sup>And when a great crowd was gathering and people from town after town came to him, he said in a parable,",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25242H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25242H\"></sup>“A sower went out to sow his seed. And as he sowed, some fell along the path and was trampled underfoot, and the birds of the air devoured it.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And some fell on the rock, and as it grew up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25243I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25243I\"></sup>it withered away, because it had no moisture.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And some fell among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25244J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25244J\"></sup>thorns, and the thorns grew up with it and choked it.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And some fell into good soil and grew and yielded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25245K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25245K\"></sup>a hundredfold.”</span> As he said these things, he called out, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25245L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25245L\"></sup>“He who has ears to hear, let him hear.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when his disciples asked him what this parable meant,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25247M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25247M\"></sup>“To you it has been given to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25247N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25247N\"></sup>the secrets of the kingdom of God, but for others they are in parables, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25247O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25247O\"></sup>that ‘seeing they may not see, and hearing they may not understand.’</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25248P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25248P\"></sup>Now the parable is this: The seed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25248Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25248Q\"></sup>the word of God.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The ones along the path are those who have heard; then the devil comes and takes away the word from their hearts, so that they may not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25249R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25249R\"></sup>believe and be saved.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the ones on the rock are those who, when they hear the word, receive it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25250S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25250S\"></sup>with joy. But these have no root; they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25250T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25250T\"></sup>believe for a while, and in time of testing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25250U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25250U\"></sup>fall away.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And as for what fell among the thorns, they are those who hear, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25251V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25251V\"></sup>as they go on their way they are choked by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25251W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25251W\"></sup>cares and riches and pleasures of life, and their fruit does not mature.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As for that in the good soil, they are those who, hearing the word, hold it fast in an honest and good heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25252X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25252X\"></sup>bear fruit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25252Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25252Y\"></sup>with patience.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25253Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25253Z\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25253AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25253AA\"></sup>“No one after lighting a lamp covers it with a jar or puts it under a bed, but puts it on a stand, so that those who enter may see the light.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25254AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25254AB\"></sup>For nothing is hidden that will not be made manifest, nor is anything secret that will not be known and come to light.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25255AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25255AC\"></sup>Take care then how you hear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25255AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25255AD\"></sup>for to the one who has, more will be given, and from the one who has not, even what he thinks that he has will be taken away.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25256AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25256AE\"></sup>Then his mother and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25256AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25256AF\"></sup>his brothers came to him, but they could not reach him because of the crowd.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he was told, “Your mother and your brothers are standing outside, desiring to see you.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“My mother and my brothers are those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25258AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25258AG\"></sup>who hear the word of God and do it.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25259AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25259AH\"></sup>One day he got into a boat with his disciples, and he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Let us go across to the other side of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25259AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25259AI\"></sup>the lake.”</span> So they set out,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and as they sailed he fell asleep. And a windstorm came down on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25260AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25260AJ\"></sup>the lake, and they were filling with water and were in danger.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they went and woke him, saying, “Master, Master, we are perishing!” And he awoke and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25261AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25261AK\"></sup>rebuked the wind and the raging waves, and they ceased, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25261AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25261AL\"></sup>and there was a calm.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Where is your faith?”</span> And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25262AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25262AM\"></sup>were afraid, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25262AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25262AN\"></sup>marveled, saying to one another, “Who then is this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25262AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25262AO\"></sup>he commands even winds and water, and they obey him?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25263AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25263AP\"></sup>Then they sailed to the country of the Gerasenes, which is opposite Galilee.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When Jesus had stepped out on land, there met him a man from the city who had demons. For a long time he had worn no clothes, and he had not lived in a house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25264AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25264AQ\"></sup>but among the tombs.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When he saw Jesus, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25265AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25265AR\"></sup>cried out and fell down before him and said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25265AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25265AS\"></sup>with a loud voice, “What have you to do with me, Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25265AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25265AT\"></sup>Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25265AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25265AU\"></sup>the Most High God? I beg you, do not torment me.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For he had commanded the unclean spirit to come out of the man. (For many a time it had seized him. He was kept under guard and bound with chains and shackles, but he would break the bonds and be driven by the demon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25266AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25266AV\"></sup>into the desert.)",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Jesus then asked him, <span class=\"woj\">“What is your name?”</span> And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25267AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25267AW\"></sup>“Legion,” for many demons had entered him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And they begged him not to command them to depart into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25268AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25268AX\"></sup>the abyss.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now a large herd of pigs was feeding there on the hillside, and they begged him to let them enter these. So he gave them permission.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Then the demons came out of the man and entered the pigs, and the herd rushed down the steep bank into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25270AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25270AY\"></sup>the lake and drowned.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When the herdsmen saw what had happened, they fled and told it in the city and in the country.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then people went out to see what had happened, and they came to Jesus and found the man from whom the demons had gone, sitting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25272AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25272AZ\"></sup>at the feet of Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25272BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25272BA\"></sup>clothed and in his right mind, and they were afraid.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And those who had seen it told them how the demon-possessed man had been healed.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Then all the people of the surrounding country of the Gerasenes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25274BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25274BB\"></sup>asked him to depart from them, for they were seized with great fear. So he got into the boat and returned.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>The man from whom the demons had gone begged that he might be with him, but Jesus sent him away, saying,",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“Return to your home, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25276BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25276BC\"></sup>declare how much God has done for you.”</span> And he went away, proclaiming throughout the whole city how much Jesus had done for him.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Now when Jesus returned, the crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25277BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25277BD\"></sup>welcomed him, for they were all waiting for him.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25278BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25278BE\"></sup>And there came a man named Jairus, who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25278BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25278BF\"></sup>a ruler of the synagogue. And falling at Jesus' feet, he implored him to come to his house,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>for he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25279BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25279BG\"></sup>an only daughter, about twelve years of age, and she was dying.As Jesus went, the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25279BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25279BH\"></sup>pressed around him.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And there was a woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25280BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25280BI\"></sup>who had had a discharge of blood for twelve years, and though she had spent all her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25280BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25280BJ\"></sup>living on physicians, she could not be healed by anyone.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>She came up behind him and touched <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25281BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25281BK\"></sup>the fringe of his garment, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25281BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25281BL\"></sup>immediately her discharge of blood ceased.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Who was it that touched me?”</span> When all denied it, Peter said, “Master, the crowds surround you and are pressing in on you!”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>But Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Someone touched me, for I perceive that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25283BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25283BM\"></sup>power has gone out from me.”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And when the woman saw that she was not hidden, she came trembling, and falling down before him declared in the presence of all the people why she had touched him, and how she had been immediately healed.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And he said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Daughter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25285BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25285BN\"></sup>your faith has made you well; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25285BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25285BO\"></sup>go in peace.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>While he was still speaking, someone from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25286BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25286BP\"></sup>the ruler's house came and said, “Your daughter is dead; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25286BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25286BQ\"></sup>do not trouble <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25286BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25286BR\"></sup>the Teacher any more.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>But Jesus on hearing this answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not fear; only believe, and she will be well.”</span>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And when he came to the house, he allowed no one to enter with him, except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25288BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25288BS\"></sup>Peter and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25288BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25288BT\"></sup>John and James, and the father and mother of the child.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And all were weeping and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25289BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25289BU\"></sup>mourning for her, but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25289BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25289BV\"></sup>said, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not weep, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25289BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25289BW\"></sup>she is not dead but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25289BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25289BX\"></sup>sleeping.”</span>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>And they laughed at him, knowing that she was dead.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25291BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25291BY\"></sup>taking her by the hand he called, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Child, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25291BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25291BZ\"></sup>arise.”</span>",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25292CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25292CA\"></sup>her spirit returned, and she got up at once. And he directed that something should be given her to eat.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And her parents were amazed, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25293CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25293CB\"></sup>he charged them to tell no one what had happened."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25294A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25294A\"></sup>And he called the twelve together and gave them power and authority over all demons and to cure diseases,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25295B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25295B\"></sup>and he sent them out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25295C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25295C\"></sup>proclaim the kingdom of God and to heal.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25296D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25296D\"></sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Take nothing for your journey, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25296E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25296E\"></sup>no staff, nor bag, nor bread, nor money; and do not have two tunics.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And whatever house you enter, stay there, and from there depart.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And wherever they do not receive you, when you leave that town <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25298F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25298F\"></sup>shake off the dust from your feet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25298G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25298G\"></sup>as a testimony <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25298H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25298H\"></sup>against them.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25299I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25299I\"></sup>And they departed and went through the villages, preaching the gospel and healing everywhere.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25300J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25300J\"></sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25300K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25300K\"></sup>Herod the tetrarch heard about all that was happening, and he was perplexed, because it was said by some that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25300L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25300L\"></sup>John had been raised from the dead,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25301M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25301M\"></sup>by some that Elijah had appeared, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25301N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25301N\"></sup>by others that one of the prophets of old had risen.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Herod said, “John I beheaded, but who is this about whom I hear such things?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25302O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25302O\"></sup>he sought to see him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>On their return <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25303P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25303P\"></sup>the apostles told him all that they had done. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25303Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25303Q\"></sup>And he took them and withdrew apart to a town called Bethsaida.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When the crowds learned it, they followed him, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25304R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25304R\"></sup>welcomed them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25304S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25304S\"></sup>spoke to them of the kingdom of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25304T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25304T\"></sup>cured those who had need of healing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25305U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25305U\"></sup>the day began to wear away, and the twelve came and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25305V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25305V\"></sup>“Send the crowd away to go into the surrounding villages and countryside to find lodging and get provisions, for we are here in a desolate place.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25306W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25306W\"></sup>“You give them something to eat.”</span> They said, “We have no more than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25306X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25306X\"></sup>five loaves and two fish—unless we are to go and buy food for all these people.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For there were about five thousand men. And he said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Have them sit down in groups of about fifty each.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And they did so, and had them all sit down.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And taking the five loaves and the two fish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25309Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25309Y\"></sup>he looked up to heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25309Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25309Z\"></sup>said a blessing over them. Then he broke the loaves and gave them to the disciples to set before the crowd.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they all ate and were satisfied. And what was left over was picked up, twelve baskets of broken pieces.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25311AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25311AA\"></sup>Now it happened that as he was praying alone, the disciples were with him. And he asked them, <span class=\"woj\">“Who do the crowds say that I am?”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25312AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25312AB\"></sup>“John the Baptist. But others say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25312AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25312AC\"></sup>Elijah, and others, that one of the prophets of old has risen.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“But who do you say that I am?”</span> And Peter answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25313AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25313AD\"></sup>“The Christ of God.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25314AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25314AE\"></sup>And he strictly charged and commanded them to tell this to no one,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25315AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25315AF\"></sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25315AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25315AG\"></sup>“The Son of Man must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25315AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25315AH\"></sup>suffer many things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25315AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25315AI\"></sup>be rejected by the elders and chief priests and scribes, and be killed, and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25315AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25315AJ\"></sup>the third day be raised.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he said to all, <span class=\"woj\">“If anyone would come after me, let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25316AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25316AK\"></sup>deny himself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25316AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25316AL\"></sup>take up his cross <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25316AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25316AM\"></sup>daily and follow me.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25317AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25317AN\"></sup>whoever would save his life will lose it, but whoever loses his life for my sake will save it.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25318AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25318AO\"></sup>For what does it profit a man if he gains the whole world and loses or forfeits himself?</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25319AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25319AP\"></sup>whoever is ashamed of me and of my words, of him will the Son of Man be ashamed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25319AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25319AQ\"></sup>when he comes in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25319AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25319AR\"></sup>his glory and the glory of the Father and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25319AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25319AS\"></sup>the holy angels.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But I tell you truly, there are some standing here who will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25320AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25320AT\"></sup>taste death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25320AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25320AU\"></sup>until they see the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25321AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25321AV\"></sup>Now about eight days after these sayings he took with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25321AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25321AW\"></sup>Peter and John and James and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25321AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25321AX\"></sup>went up on the mountain to pray.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And as he was praying, the appearance of his face was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25322AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25322AY\"></sup>altered, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25322AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25322AZ\"></sup>his clothing became dazzling white.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And behold, two men were talking with him, Moses and Elijah,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>who appeared in glory and spoke of his departure, which he was about to accomplish at Jerusalem.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now Peter and those who were with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25325BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25325BA\"></sup>were heavy with sleep, but when they became fully awake <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25325BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25325BB\"></sup>they saw his glory and the two men who stood with him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And as the men were parting from him, Peter said to Jesus, “Master, it is good that we are here. Let us make three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25326BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25326BC\"></sup>tents, one for you and one for Moses and one for Elijah”—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25326BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25326BD\"></sup>not knowing what he said.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>As he was saying these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25327BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25327BE\"></sup>a cloud came and overshadowed them, and they were afraid as they entered the cloud.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25328BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25328BF\"></sup>a voice came out of the cloud, saying, “This is my Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25328BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25328BG\"></sup>my Chosen One; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25328BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25328BH\"></sup>listen to him!”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And when the voice had spoken, Jesus was found alone. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25329BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25329BI\"></sup>And they kept silent and told no one in those days anything of what they had seen.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25330BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25330BJ\"></sup>On the next day, when they had come down from the mountain, a great crowd met him.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And behold, a man from the crowd cried out, “Teacher, I beg you to look at my son, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25331BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25331BK\"></sup>he is my only child.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And behold, a spirit seizes him, and he suddenly cries out. It convulses him so that he foams at the mouth, and shatters him, and will hardly leave him.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And I begged your disciples to cast it out, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25333BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25333BL\"></sup>they could not.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25334BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25334BM\"></sup>faithless and twisted generation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25334BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25334BN\"></sup>how long am I to be with you and bear with you? Bring your son here.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>While he was coming, the demon threw him to the ground and convulsed him. But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25335BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25335BO\"></sup>rebuked the unclean spirit and healed the boy, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25335BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25335BP\"></sup>gave him back to his father.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And all were astonished at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25336BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25336BQ\"></sup>the majesty of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25336BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25336BR\"></sup>But while they were all marveling at everything he was doing, Jesus said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25336BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25336BS\"></sup>to his disciples,",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“Let these words sink into your ears: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25337BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25337BT\"></sup>The Son of Man is about to be delivered into the hands of men.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25338BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25338BU\"></sup>But they did not understand this saying, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25338BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25338BV\"></sup>it was concealed from them, so that they might not perceive it. And they were afraid to ask him about this saying.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25339BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25339BW\"></sup>An argument arose among them as to which of them was the greatest.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>But Jesus, knowing the reasoning of their hearts, took a child and put him by his side",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25341BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25341BX\"></sup>“Whoever receives this child in my name receives me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25341BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25341BY\"></sup>whoever receives me receives him who sent me. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25341BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25341BZ\"></sup>he who is least among you all is the one who is great.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25342CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25342CA\"></sup>John answered, “Master, we saw someone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25342CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25342CB\"></sup>casting out demons in your name, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25342CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25342CC\"></sup>we tried to stop him, because he does not follow with us.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>But Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not stop him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25343CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25343CD\"></sup>for the one who is not against you is for you.”</span>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>When the days drew near for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25344CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25344CE\"></sup>him to be taken up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25344CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25344CF\"></sup>he set his face <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25344CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25344CG\"></sup>to go to Jerusalem.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25345CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25345CH\"></sup>he sent messengers ahead of him, who went and entered a village of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25345CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25345CI\"></sup>the Samaritans, to make preparations for him.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25346CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25346CJ\"></sup>the people did not receive him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25346CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25346CK\"></sup>his face was set toward Jerusalem.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>And when his disciples James and John saw it, they said, “Lord, do you want us to tell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25347CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25347CL\"></sup>fire to come down from heaven and consume them?”",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>But he turned and rebuked them.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And they went on to another village.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>As they were going <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25350CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25350CM\"></sup>along the road, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25350CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25350CN\"></sup>someone said to him, “I will follow you wherever you go.”",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Foxes have holes, and birds of the air have nests, but the Son of Man has nowhere to lay his head.”</span>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>To another he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me.”</span> But he said, “Lord, let me first go and bury my father.”",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Leave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25353CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25353CO\"></sup>the dead to bury their own dead. But as for you, go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25353CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25353CP\"></sup>proclaim the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>Yet another said, “I will follow you, Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25354CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25354CQ\"></sup>but let me first say farewell to those at my home.”",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25355CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25355CR\"></sup>“No one who puts his hand to the plow and looks back is fit for the kingdom of God.”</span>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>After this the Lord appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25356A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25356A\"></sup>seventy-two others and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25356B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25356B\"></sup>sent them on ahead of him, two by two, into every town and place where he himself was about to go.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25357C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25357C\"></sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“The harvest is plentiful, but the laborers are few. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25357D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25357D\"></sup>Therefore pray earnestly to the Lord of the harvest to send out laborers into his harvest.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Go your way; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25358E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25358E\"></sup>behold, I am sending you out as lambs in the midst of wolves.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25359F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25359F\"></sup>Carry no moneybag, no knapsack, no sandals, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25359G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25359G\"></sup>greet no one on the road.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Whatever house you enter, first say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25360H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25360H\"></sup>‘Peace be to this house!’</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And if a son of peace is there, your peace will rest upon him. But if not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25361I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25361I\"></sup>it will return to you.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And remain in the same house, eating and drinking what they provide, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25362J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25362J\"></sup>the laborer deserves his wages. Do not go from house to house.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whenever you enter a town and they receive you, eat what is set before you.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Heal the sick in it and say to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25364K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25364K\"></sup>‘The kingdom of God has come near to you.’</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But whenever you enter a town and they do not receive you, go into its streets and say,</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25366L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25366L\"></sup>‘Even the dust of your town that clings to our feet we wipe off against you. Nevertheless know this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25366M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25366M\"></sup>the kingdom of God has come near.’</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25367N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25367N\"></sup>it will be more bearable on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25367O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25367O\"></sup>that day for Sodom than for that town.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25368P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25368P\"></sup>“Woe to you, Chorazin! Woe to you, Bethsaida! For if the mighty works done in you had been done in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25368Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25368Q\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon, they would have repented long ago, sitting in sackcloth and ashes.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25369R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25369R\"></sup>But it will be more bearable in the judgment for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25369S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25369S\"></sup>Tyre and Sidon than for you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And you, Capernaum, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25370T\"></sup>will you be exalted to heaven? You shall be brought down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25370U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25370U\"></sup>Hades.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25371V\"></sup>“The one who hears you hears me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25371W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25371W\"></sup>the one who rejects you rejects me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25371X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25371X\"></sup>the one who rejects me rejects him who sent me.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25372Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25372Y\"></sup>The seventy-two returned with joy, saying, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25372Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25372Z\"></sup>even the demons are subject to us in your name!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25373AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25373AA\"></sup>“I saw Satan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25373AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25373AB\"></sup>fall like lightning from heaven.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Behold, I have given you authority <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25374AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25374AC\"></sup>to tread on serpents and scorpions, and over all the power of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25374AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25374AD\"></sup>the enemy, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25374AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25374AE\"></sup>nothing shall hurt you.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25375AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25375AF\"></sup>Nevertheless, do not rejoice in this, that the spirits are subject to you, but rejoice that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25375AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25375AG\"></sup>your names are written in heaven.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AH\"></sup>In that same hour <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AI\"></sup>he rejoiced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AJ\"></sup>in the Holy Spirit and said, <span class=\"woj\">“I thank you, Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AK\"></sup>Lord of heaven and earth, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AL\"></sup>you have hidden these things from the wise and understanding and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AM\"></sup>revealed them to little children; yes, Father, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25376AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25376AN\"></sup>such was your gracious will.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25377AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25377AO\"></sup>All things have been handed over to me by my Father, and no one knows who the Son is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25377AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25377AP\"></sup>except the Father, or who the Father is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25377AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25377AQ\"></sup>except the Son and anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25377AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25377AR\"></sup>to whom the Son chooses to reveal him.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then turning to the disciples he said privately, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25378AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25378AS\"></sup>“Blessed are the eyes that see what you see!</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For I tell you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25379AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25379AT\"></sup>that many prophets and kings desired to see what you see, and did not see it, and to hear what you hear, and did not hear it.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25380AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25380AU\"></sup>And behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25380AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25380AV\"></sup>lawyer stood up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25380AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25380AW\"></sup>put him to the test, saying, “Teacher, what shall I do to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25380AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25380AX\"></sup>inherit eternal life?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“What is written in the Law? How do you read it?”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25382AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25382AY\"></sup>“You shall love the Lord your God with all your heart and with all your soul and with all your strength and with all your mind, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25382AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25382AZ\"></sup>your neighbor as yourself.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You have answered correctly; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25383BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25383BA\"></sup>do this, and you will live.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But he, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25384BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25384BB\"></sup>desiring to justify himself, said to Jesus, “And who is my neighbor?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Jesus replied, <span class=\"woj\">“A man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25385BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25385BC\"></sup>was going down from Jerusalem to Jericho, and he fell among robbers, who stripped him and beat him and departed, leaving him half dead.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Now by chance a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25386BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25386BD\"></sup>priest was going down that road, and when he saw him he passed by on the other side.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So likewise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25387BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25387BE\"></sup>a Levite, when he came to the place and saw him, passed by on the other side.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25388BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25388BF\"></sup>Samaritan, as he journeyed, came to where he was, and when he saw him, he had compassion.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He went to him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25389BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25389BG\"></sup>bound up his wounds, pouring on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25389BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25389BH\"></sup>oil and wine. Then he set him on his own animal and brought him to an inn and took care of him.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And the next day he took out two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25390BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25390BI\"></sup>denarii and gave them to the innkeeper, saying, ‘Take care of him, and whatever more you spend, I will repay you when I come back.’</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Which of these three, do you think, proved to be a neighbor to the man who fell among the robbers?”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>He said, “The one who showed him mercy.” And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You go, and do likewise.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Now as they went on their way, Jesus entered a village. And a woman named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25393BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25393BJ\"></sup>Martha <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25393BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25393BK\"></sup>welcomed him into her house.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And she had a sister called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25394BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25394BL\"></sup>Mary, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25394BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25394BM\"></sup>sat at the Lord's feet and listened to his teaching.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But Martha was distracted with much serving. And she went up to him and said, “Lord, do you not care that my sister has left me to serve alone? Tell her then to help me.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>But the Lord answered her, <span class=\"woj\">“Martha, Martha, you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25396BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25396BN\"></sup>anxious and troubled about many things,</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>but one thing is necessary. Mary has chosen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25397BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25397BO\"></sup>the good portion, which will not be taken away from her.”</span>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now Jesus was praying in a certain place, and when he finished, one of his disciples said to him, “Lord, teach us to pray, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25398A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25398A\"></sup>as John taught his disciples.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25399B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25399B\"></sup>“When you pray, say:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25399C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25399C\"></sup>“Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25399D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25399D\"></sup>hallowed be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25399E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25399E\"></sup>your name.</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25399F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25399F\"></sup>Your kingdom come.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25400G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25400G\"></sup>Give us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25400H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25400H\"></sup>each day our daily bread,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25401I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25401I\"></sup>forgive us our sins,</span><span class=\"woj\">for we ourselves forgive everyone who is indebted to us.</span><span class=\"woj\">And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25401J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25401J\"></sup>lead us not into temptation.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Which of you who has a friend will go to him at midnight and say to him, ‘Friend, lend me three loaves,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>for a friend of mine has arrived on a journey, and I have nothing to set before him’;</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and he will answer from within, ‘Do not bother me; the door is now shut, and my children are with me in bed. I cannot get up and give you anything’?</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I tell you, though he will not get up and give him anything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25405K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25405K\"></sup>because he is his friend, yet because of his impudence he will rise and give him whatever he needs.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25406L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25406L\"></sup>ask, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25406M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25406M\"></sup>it will be given to you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25406N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25406N\"></sup>seek, and you will find; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25406O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25406O\"></sup>knock, and it will be opened to you.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For everyone who asks receives, and the one who seeks finds, and to the one who knocks it will be opened.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>What father among you, if his son asks for a fish, will instead of a fish give him a serpent;</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>or if he asks for an egg, will give him a scorpion?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If you then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25410P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25410P\"></sup>who are evil, know how to give good gifts to your children, how much more will the heavenly Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25410Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25410Q\"></sup>give the Holy Spirit to those who ask him!”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25411R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25411R\"></sup>Now he was casting out a demon that was mute. When the demon had gone out, the mute man spoke, and the people marveled.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But some of them said, “He casts out demons <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25412S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25412S\"></sup>by Beelzebul, the prince of demons,”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>while others, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25413T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25413T\"></sup>to test him, kept seeking from him a sign from heaven.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25414U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25414U\"></sup>But he, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25414V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25414V\"></sup>knowing their thoughts, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Every kingdom divided against itself is laid waste, and a divided household falls.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And if Satan also is divided against himself, how will his kingdom stand? For you say that I cast out demons by Beelzebul.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And if I cast out demons by Beelzebul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25416W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25416W\"></sup>by whom do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25416X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25416X\"></sup>your sons cast them out? Therefore they will be your judges.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But if it is by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25417Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25417Y\"></sup>the finger of God that I cast out demons, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25417Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25417Z\"></sup>the kingdom of God has come upon you.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When a strong man, fully armed, guards his own palace, his goods are safe;</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25419AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25419AA\"></sup>but when one stronger than he attacks him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25419AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25419AB\"></sup>overcomes him, he takes away his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25419AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25419AC\"></sup>armor in which he trusted and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25419AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25419AD\"></sup>divides his spoil.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25420AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25420AE\"></sup>Whoever is not with me is against me, and whoever does not gather with me scatters.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25421AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25421AF\"></sup>“When the unclean spirit has gone out of a person, it passes through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25421AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25421AG\"></sup>waterless places seeking rest, and finding none it says, ‘I will return to my house from which I came.’</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And when it comes, it finds the house swept and put in order.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then it goes and brings seven other spirits more evil than itself, and they enter and dwell there. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25423AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25423AH\"></sup>the last state of that person is worse than the first.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>As he said these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25424AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25424AI\"></sup>a woman in the crowd raised her voice and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25424AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25424AJ\"></sup>“Blessed is the womb that bore you, and the breasts at which you nursed!”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25425AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25425AK\"></sup>“Blessed rather are those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25425AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25425AL\"></sup>who hear the word of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25425AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25425AM\"></sup>keep it!”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25426AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25426AN\"></sup>When the crowds were increasing, he began to say, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25426AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25426AO\"></sup>“This generation is an evil generation. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25426AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25426AP\"></sup>It seeks for a sign, but no sign will be given to it except the sign of Jonah.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25427AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25427AQ\"></sup>Jonah became a sign to the people of Nineveh, so will the Son of Man be to this generation.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25428AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25428AR\"></sup>The queen of the South will rise up at the judgment with the men of this generation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25428AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25428AS\"></sup>condemn them, for she came from the ends of the earth to hear the wisdom of Solomon, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25428AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25428AT\"></sup>something greater than Solomon is here.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25429AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25429AU\"></sup>The men of Nineveh will rise up at the judgment with this generation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25429AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25429AV\"></sup>condemn it, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25429AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25429AW\"></sup>they repented at the preaching of Jonah, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25429AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25429AX\"></sup>something greater than Jonah is here.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25430AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25430AY\"></sup>“No one after lighting a lamp puts it in a cellar or under a basket, but on a stand, so that those who enter may see the light.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Your eye is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25431AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25431AZ\"></sup>the lamp of your body. When your eye is healthy, your whole body is full of light, but when it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25431BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25431BA\"></sup>bad, your body is full of darkness.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25432BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25432BB\"></sup>Therefore be careful lest the light in you be darkness.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>If then your whole body is full of light, having no part dark, it will be wholly bright, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25433BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25433BC\"></sup>as when a lamp with its rays gives you light.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>While Jesus was speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25434BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25434BD\"></sup>a Pharisee asked him to dine with him, so he went in and reclined at table.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>The Pharisee was astonished to see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25435BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25435BE\"></sup>that he did not first wash before dinner.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And the Lord said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25436BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25436BF\"></sup>“Now you Pharisees cleanse the outside of the cup and of the dish, but inside you are full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25436BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25436BG\"></sup>greed and wickedness.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25437BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25437BH\"></sup>You fools! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25437BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25437BI\"></sup>Did not he who made the outside make the inside also?</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25438BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25438BJ\"></sup>give as alms those things that are within, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25438BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25438BK\"></sup>everything is clean for you.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25439BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25439BL\"></sup>“But woe to you Pharisees! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25439BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25439BM\"></sup>you tithe mint and rue and every herb, and neglect <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25439BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25439BN\"></sup>justice and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25439BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25439BO\"></sup>the love of God. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25439BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25439BP\"></sup>These you ought to have done, without neglecting the others.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Woe to you Pharisees! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25440BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25440BQ\"></sup>you love the best seat in the synagogues and greetings in the marketplaces.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Woe to you! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25441BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25441BR\"></sup>For you are like unmarked graves, and people walk over them without knowing it.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>One of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25442BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25442BS\"></sup>the lawyers answered him, “Teacher, in saying these things you insult us also.”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Woe to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25443BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25443BT\"></sup>lawyers also! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25443BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25443BU\"></sup>you load people with burdens hard to bear, and you yourselves do not touch the burdens with one of your fingers.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25444BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25444BV\"></sup>Woe to you! For you build the tombs of the prophets whom your fathers killed.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25445BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25445BW\"></sup>So you are witnesses and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25445BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25445BX\"></sup>consent to the deeds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25445BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25445BY\"></sup>your fathers, for they killed them, and you build their tombs.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Therefore also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25446BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25446BZ\"></sup>the Wisdom of God said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25446CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25446CA\"></sup>‘I will send them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25446CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25446CB\"></sup>prophets and apostles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25446CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25446CC\"></sup>some of whom they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25446CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25446CD\"></sup>kill and persecute,’</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25447CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25447CE\"></sup>the blood of all the prophets, shed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25447CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25447CF\"></sup>from the foundation of the world, may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25447CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25447CG\"></sup>charged against this generation,</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>from the blood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25448CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25448CH\"></sup>Abel to the blood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25448CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25448CI\"></sup>Zechariah, who perished between <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25448CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25448CJ\"></sup>the altar and the sanctuary. Yes, I tell you, it will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25448CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25448CK\"></sup>required of this generation.</span>",
			"52": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Woe to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25449CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25449CL\"></sup>lawyers! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25449CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25449CM\"></sup>For you have taken away the key of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25449CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25449CN\"></sup>knowledge. You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25449CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25449CO\"></sup>did not enter yourselves, and you hindered those who were entering.”</span>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>As he went away from there, the scribes and the Pharisees began to press him hard and to provoke him to speak about many things,",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25451CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25451CP\"></sup>lying in wait for him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25451CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25451CQ\"></sup>to catch him in something he might say."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>In the meantime, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25452A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25452A\"></sup>when so many thousands of the people had gathered together that they were trampling one another, he began to say to his disciples first, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25452B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25452B\"></sup>“Beware of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25452C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25452C\"></sup>the leaven of the Pharisees, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25452D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25452D\"></sup>which is hypocrisy.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25453E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25453E\"></sup>Nothing is covered up that will not be revealed, or hidden that will not be known.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore whatever you have said in the dark shall be heard in the light, and what you have whispered in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25454F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25454F\"></sup>private rooms shall be proclaimed on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25454G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25454G\"></sup>the housetops.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I tell you, my friends, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25455H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25455H\"></sup>do not fear those who kill the body, and after that have nothing more that they can do.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But I will warn you whom to fear: fear him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25456I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25456I\"></sup>who, after he has killed, has authority to cast into hell. Yes, I tell you, fear him!</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Are not five sparrows sold for two pennies? And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25457J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25457J\"></sup>not one of them is forgotten before God.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Why, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25458K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25458K\"></sup>even the hairs of your head are all numbered. Fear not; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25458L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25458L\"></sup>you are of more value than many sparrows.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25459M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25459M\"></sup>everyone who acknowledges me before men, the Son of Man also will acknowledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25459N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25459N\"></sup>before the angels of God,</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25460O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25460O\"></sup>the one who denies me before men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25460P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25460P\"></sup>will be denied <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25460Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25460Q\"></sup>before the angels of God.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25461R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25461R\"></sup>everyone who speaks a word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25461S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25461S\"></sup>against the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25461T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25461T\"></sup>will be forgiven, but the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25461U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25461U\"></sup>blasphemes against the Holy Spirit will not be forgiven.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25462V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25462V\"></sup>And when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25462W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25462W\"></sup>bring you before the synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25462X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25462X\"></sup>the rulers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25462Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25462Y\"></sup>the authorities, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25462Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25462Z\"></sup>do not be anxious about how you should defend yourself or what you should say,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25463AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25463AA\"></sup>for the Holy Spirit will teach you in that very hour what you ought to say.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25464AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25464AB\"></sup>Someone in the crowd said to him, “Teacher, tell my brother to divide the inheritance with me.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But he said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25465AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25465AC\"></sup>“Man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25465AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25465AD\"></sup>who made me a judge or arbitrator over you?”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25466AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25466AE\"></sup>“Take care, and be on your guard against all covetousness, for one's life does not consist in the abundance of his possessions.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he told them a parable, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25467AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25467AF\"></sup>“The land of a rich man produced plentifully,</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and he thought to himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25468AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25468AG\"></sup>‘What shall I do, for I have nowhere to store my crops?’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And he said, ‘I will do this: I will tear down my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25469AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25469AH\"></sup>barns and build larger ones, and there I will store all my grain and my goods.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I will say to my soul, “Soul, you have ample goods laid up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25470AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25470AI\"></sup>for many years; relax, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25470AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25470AJ\"></sup>eat, drink, be merry.”’</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But God said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25471AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25471AK\"></sup>‘Fool! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25471AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25471AL\"></sup>This night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25471AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25471AM\"></sup>your soul is required of you, and the things you have prepared, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25471AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25471AN\"></sup>whose will they be?’</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So is the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25472AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25472AO\"></sup>who lays up treasure for himself and is not rich toward God.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And he said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25473AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25473AP\"></sup>“Therefore I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25473AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25473AQ\"></sup>do not be anxious about your life, what you will eat, nor about your body, what you will put on.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For life is more than food, and the body more than clothing.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25475AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25475AR\"></sup>Consider the ravens: they neither sow nor reap, they have neither storehouse nor barn, and yet God feeds them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25475AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25475AS\"></sup>Of how much more value are you than the birds!</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And which of you by being anxious can add a single hour to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25476AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25476AT\"></sup>span of life?</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If then you are not able to do as small a thing as that, why are you anxious about the rest?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Consider the lilies, how they grow: they neither toil nor spin, yet I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25478AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25478AU\"></sup>even Solomon in all his glory was not arrayed like one of these.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if God so clothes the grass, which is alive in the field today, and tomorrow is thrown into the oven, how much more will he clothe you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25479AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25479AV\"></sup>O you of little faith!</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And do not seek what you are to eat and what you are to drink, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25480AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25480AW\"></sup>be worried.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25481AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25481AX\"></sup>all the nations of the world seek after these things, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25481AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25481AY\"></sup>your Father knows that you need them.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Instead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25482AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25482AZ\"></sup>seek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25482BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25482BA\"></sup>his kingdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25482BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25482BB\"></sup>and these things will be added to you.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25483BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25483BC\"></sup>“Fear not, little <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25483BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25483BD\"></sup>flock, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25483BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25483BE\"></sup>it is your Father's good pleasure to give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25483BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25483BF\"></sup>the kingdom.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25484BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25484BG\"></sup>Sell your possessions, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25484BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25484BH\"></sup>give to the needy. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25484BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25484BI\"></sup>Provide yourselves with moneybags that do not grow old, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25484BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25484BJ\"></sup>a treasure in the heavens that does not fail, where no thief approaches and no moth destroys.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25485BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25485BK\"></sup>For where your treasure is, there will your heart be also.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25486BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25486BL\"></sup>“Stay dressed for action and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25486BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25486BM\"></sup>keep your lamps burning,</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and be like men who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25487BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25487BN\"></sup>waiting for their master to come home from the wedding feast, so that they may open the door to him at once when he comes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25487BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25487BO\"></sup>knocks.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25488BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25488BP\"></sup>Blessed are those servants whom the master finds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25488BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25488BQ\"></sup>awake when he comes. Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25488BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25488BR\"></sup>he will dress himself for service and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25488BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25488BS\"></sup>have them recline at table, and he will come and serve them.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>If he comes in the second watch, or in the third, and finds them awake, blessed are those servants!</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25490BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25490BT\"></sup>But know this, that if the master of the house had known at what hour <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25490BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25490BU\"></sup>the thief was coming, he would not have left his house to be broken into.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>You also must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25491BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25491BV\"></sup>ready, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25491BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25491BW\"></sup>the Son of Man is coming at an hour you do not expect.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Peter said, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25492BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25492BX\"></sup>are you telling this parable for us or for all?”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And the Lord said, <span class=\"woj\">“Who then is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25493BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25493BY\"></sup>the faithful and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25493BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25493BZ\"></sup>wise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25493CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25493CA\"></sup>manager, whom his master will set over his household, to give them their portion of food at the proper time?</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25494CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25494CB\"></sup>Blessed is that servant whom his master will find so doing when he comes.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25495CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25495CC\"></sup>he will set him over all his possessions.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>But if that servant says to himself, ‘My master <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25496CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25496CD\"></sup>is delayed in coming,’ and begins to beat the male and female servants, and to eat and drink and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25496CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25496CE\"></sup>get drunk,</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>the master of that servant will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25497CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25497CF\"></sup>on a day when he does not expect him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25497CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25497CG\"></sup>at an hour he does not know, and will cut him in pieces and put him with the unfaithful.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25498CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25498CH\"></sup>And that servant who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25498CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25498CI\"></sup>knew his master's will but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25498CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25498CJ\"></sup>did not get ready <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25498CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25498CK\"></sup>or act according to his will, will receive a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25498CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25498CL\"></sup>severe beating.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25499CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25499CM\"></sup>But the one who did not know, and did what deserved a beating, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25499CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25499CN\"></sup>will receive a light beating. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25499CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25499CO\"></sup>Everyone to whom much was given, of him much will be required, and from him to whom they entrusted much, they will demand the more.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25500CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25500CP\"></sup>“I came to cast fire on the earth, and would that it were already kindled!</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25501CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25501CQ\"></sup>I have a baptism to be baptized with, and how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25501CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25501CR\"></sup>great is my distress until it is accomplished!</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25502CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25502CS\"></sup>Do you think that I have come to give peace on earth? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25502CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25502CT\"></sup>No, I tell you, but rather division.</span>",
			"52": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>For from now on in one house there will be five divided, three against two and two against three.</span>",
			"53": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>They will be divided, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25504CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25504CU\"></sup>father against son and son against father, mother against daughter and daughter against mother, mother-in-law against her daughter-in-law and daughter-in-law against mother-in-law.”</span>",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>He also said to the crowds, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25505CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25505CV\"></sup>“When you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25505CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25505CW\"></sup>a cloud rising in the west, you say at once, ‘A shower is coming.’ And so it happens.</span>",
			"55": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25506CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25506CX\"></sup>when you see the south wind blowing, you say, ‘There will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25506CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25506CY\"></sup>scorching heat,’ and it happens.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>You hypocrites! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25507CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25507CZ\"></sup>You know how to interpret the appearance of earth and sky, but why do you not know how to interpret the present time?</span>",
			"57": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>“And why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25508DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25508DA\"></sup>do you not judge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25508DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25508DB\"></sup>for yourselves what is right?</span>",
			"58": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25509DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25509DC\"></sup>As you go with your accuser before the magistrate, make an effort to settle with him on the way, lest he drag you to the judge, and the judge hand you over to the officer, and the officer put you in prison.</span>",
			"59": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25510DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25510DD\"></sup>you will never get out until you have paid the very last <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25510DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25510DE\"></sup>penny.”</span>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>There were some present at that very time who told him about the Galileans whose blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25511A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25511A\"></sup>Pilate had mingled with their sacrifices.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25512B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25512B\"></sup>“Do you think that these Galileans were worse sinners than all the other Galileans, because they suffered in this way?</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>No, I tell you; but unless you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25513C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25513C\"></sup>repent, you will all likewise perish.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Or those eighteen on whom the tower in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25514D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25514D\"></sup>Siloam fell and killed them: do you think that they were worse offenders than all the others who lived in Jerusalem?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>No, I tell you; but unless you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25515E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25515E\"></sup>repent, you will all likewise perish.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he told this parable: <span class=\"woj\">“A man had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25516F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25516F\"></sup>a fig tree planted in his vineyard, and he came seeking fruit on it and found none.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he said to the vinedresser, ‘Look, for three years now I have come seeking fruit on this fig tree, and I find none. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25517G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25517G\"></sup>Cut it down. Why should it use up the ground?’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he answered him, ‘Sir, let it alone this year also, until I dig around it and put on manure.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then if it should bear fruit next year, well and good; but if not, you can cut it down.’”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25520H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25520H\"></sup>he was teaching in one of the synagogues on the Sabbath.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And behold, there was a woman who had had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25521I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25521I\"></sup>a disabling spirit for eighteen years. She was bent over and could not fully straighten herself.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When Jesus saw her, he called her over and said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Woman, you are freed from your disability.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25523J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25523J\"></sup>laid his hands on her, and immediately she was made straight, and she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25523K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25523K\"></sup>glorified God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25524L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25524L\"></sup>the ruler of the synagogue, indignant because Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25524M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25524M\"></sup>had healed on the Sabbath, said to the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25524N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25524N\"></sup>“There are six days in which work ought to be done. Come on those days and be healed, and not on the Sabbath day.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the Lord answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“You hypocrites! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25525O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25525O\"></sup>Does not each of you on the Sabbath untie his ox or his donkey from the manger and lead it away to water it?</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And ought not this woman, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25526P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25526P\"></sup>a daughter of Abraham whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25526Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25526Q\"></sup>Satan bound for eighteen years, be loosed from this bond on the Sabbath day?”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>As he said these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25527R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25527R\"></sup>all his adversaries were put to shame, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25527S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25527S\"></sup>all the people rejoiced at all the glorious things that were done by him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25528T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25528T\"></sup>He said therefore, <span class=\"woj\">“What is the kingdom of God like? And to what shall I compare it?</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25529U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25529U\"></sup>a grain of mustard seed that a man took and sowed in his garden, and it grew and became a tree, and the birds of the air made nests in its branches.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And again he said, <span class=\"woj\">“To what shall I compare the kingdom of God?</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25531V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25531V\"></sup>It is like leaven that a woman took and hid in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25531W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25531W\"></sup>three measures of flour, until it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25531X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25531X\"></sup>all leavened.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25532Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25532Y\"></sup>He went on his way through towns and villages, teaching and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25532Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25532Z\"></sup>journeying toward Jerusalem.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And someone said to him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25533AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25533AA\"></sup>will those who are saved be few?” And he said to them,",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25534AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25534AB\"></sup>“Strive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25534AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25534AC\"></sup>to enter through the narrow door. For many, I tell you, will seek to enter and will not be able.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25535AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25535AD\"></sup>When once the master of the house has risen and shut the door, and you begin to stand outside and to knock at the door, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25535AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25535AE\"></sup>‘Lord, open to us,’ then he will answer you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25535AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25535AF\"></sup>‘I do not know where you come from.’</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then you will begin to say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25536AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25536AG\"></sup>‘We ate and drank in your presence, and you taught in our streets.’</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But he will say, ‘I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25537AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25537AH\"></sup>I do not know where you come from. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25537AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25537AI\"></sup>Depart from me, all you workers of evil!’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25538AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25538AJ\"></sup>In that place there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth, when you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25538AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25538AK\"></sup>Abraham and Isaac and Jacob and all the prophets in the kingdom of God but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25538AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25538AL\"></sup>you yourselves cast out.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25539AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25539AM\"></sup>people will come from east and west, and from north and south, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25539AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25539AN\"></sup>recline at table in the kingdom of God.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25540AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25540AO\"></sup>some are last who will be first, and some are first who will be last.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>At that very hour some Pharisees came and said to him, “Get away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25541AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25541AP\"></sup>here, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25541AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25541AQ\"></sup>Herod wants to kill you.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go and tell that fox, ‘Behold, I cast out demons and perform cures today and tomorrow, and the third day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25542AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25542AR\"></sup>I finish my course.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Nevertheless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25543AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25543AS\"></sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25543AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25543AT\"></sup>must go on my way today and tomorrow and the day following, for it cannot be that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25543AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25543AU\"></sup>a prophet should perish away from Jerusalem.’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544AV\"></sup>O Jerusalem, Jerusalem, the city that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544AW\"></sup>kills the prophets and stones those who are sent to it! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544AX\"></sup>How often would I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544AY\"></sup>gathered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544AZ\"></sup>your children together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544BA\"></sup>as a hen gathers her brood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544BB\"></sup>under her wings, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25544BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25544BC\"></sup>you were not willing!</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25545BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25545BD\"></sup>your house is forsaken. And I tell you, you will not see me until you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25545BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25545BE\"></sup>‘Blessed is he who comes in the name of the Lord!’”</span>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>One Sabbath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25546A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25546A\"></sup>when he went to dine at the house of a ruler of the Pharisees, they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25546B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25546B\"></sup>watching him carefully.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And behold, there was a man before him who had dropsy.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And Jesus responded to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25548C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25548C\"></sup>the lawyers and Pharisees, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25548D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25548D\"></sup>“Is it lawful to heal on the Sabbath, or not?”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But they remained silent. Then he took him and healed him and sent him away.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25550E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25550E\"></sup>“Which of you, having a son or an ox that has fallen into a well on a Sabbath day, will not immediately pull him out?”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25551F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25551F\"></sup>And they could not reply to these things.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now he told a parable to those who were invited, when he noticed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25552G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25552G\"></sup>how they chose the places of honor, saying to them,",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“When you are invited by someone to a wedding feast, do not sit down in a place of honor, lest someone more distinguished than you be invited by him,</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and he who invited you both will come and say to you, ‘Give your place to this person,’ and then you will begin with shame to take the lowest place.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But when you are invited, go and sit in the lowest place, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25555H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25555H\"></sup>so that when your host comes he may say to you, ‘Friend, move up higher.’ Then you will be honored in the presence of all who sit at table with you.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25556I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25556I\"></sup>everyone who exalts himself will be humbled, and he who humbles himself will be exalted.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He said also to the man who had invited him, <span class=\"woj\">“When you give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25557J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25557J\"></sup>a dinner or a banquet, do not invite your friends or your brothers or your relatives or rich neighbors, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25557K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25557K\"></sup>lest they also invite you in return and you be repaid.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But when you give a feast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25558L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25558L\"></sup>invite <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25558M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25558M\"></sup>the poor, the crippled, the lame, the blind,</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and you will be blessed, because they cannot repay you. For you will be repaid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25559N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25559N\"></sup>at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25559O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25559O\"></sup>the resurrection of the just.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When one of those who reclined at table with him heard these things, he said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25560P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25560P\"></sup>“Blessed is everyone who will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25560Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25560Q\"></sup>eat bread in the kingdom of God!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But he said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25561R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25561R\"></sup>“A man once <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25561S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25561S\"></sup>gave a great banquet and invited many.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And at the time for the banquet he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25562T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25562T\"></sup>sent his servant to say to those who had been invited, ‘Come, for everything is now ready.’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But they all alike began to make excuses. The first said to him, ‘I have bought a field, and I must go out and see it. Please have me excused.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And another said, ‘I have bought five yoke of oxen, and I go to examine them. Please have me excused.’</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And another said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25565U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25565U\"></sup>‘I have married a wife, and therefore I cannot come.’</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So the servant came and reported these things to his master. Then the master of the house became angry and said to his servant, ‘Go out quickly to the streets and lanes of the city, and bring in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25566V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25566V\"></sup>the poor and crippled and blind and lame.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And the servant said, ‘Sir, what you commanded has been done, and still there is room.’</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the master said to the servant, ‘Go out to the highways and hedges and compel people to come in, that my house may be filled.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25569W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25569W\"></sup>none of those men who were invited shall taste my banquet.’”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now great crowds accompanied him, and he turned and said to them,",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25571X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25571X\"></sup>“If anyone comes to me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25571Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25571Y\"></sup>does not hate his own father and mother and wife and children and brothers and sisters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25571Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25571Z\"></sup>yes, and even his own life, he cannot be my disciple.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25572AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25572AA\"></sup>Whoever does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25572AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25572AB\"></sup>bear his own cross and come after me cannot be my disciple.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For which of you, desiring to build a tower, does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25573AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25573AC\"></sup>first sit down and count the cost, whether he has enough to complete it?</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Otherwise, when he has laid a foundation and is not able to finish, all who see it begin to mock him,</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>saying, ‘This man began to build and was not able to finish.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Or what king, going out to encounter another king in war, will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25576AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25576AD\"></sup>sit down first and deliberate whether he is able with ten thousand to meet him who comes against him with twenty thousand?</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And if not, while the other is yet a great way off, he sends a delegation and asks for terms of peace.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25578AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25578AE\"></sup>So therefore, any one of you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25578AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25578AF\"></sup>does not renounce all that he has cannot be my disciple.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25579AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25579AG\"></sup>“Salt is good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25579AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25579AH\"></sup>but if salt has lost its taste, how shall its saltiness be restored?</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>It is of no use either for the soil or for the manure pile. It is thrown away. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25580AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25580AI\"></sup>He who has ears to hear, let him hear.”</span>"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25581A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25581A\"></sup>the tax collectors and sinners were all drawing near to hear him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the Pharisees and the scribes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25582B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25582B\"></sup>grumbled, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25582C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25582C\"></sup>“This man receives sinners and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25582D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25582D\"></sup>eats with them.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So he told them this parable:",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25584E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25584E\"></sup>“What man of you, having a hundred sheep, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25584F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25584F\"></sup>if he has lost one of them, does not leave the ninety-nine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25584G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25584G\"></sup>in the open country, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25584H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25584H\"></sup>go after the one that is lost, until he finds it?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when he has found it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25585I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25585I\"></sup>he lays it on his shoulders, rejoicing.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when he comes home, he calls together his friends and his neighbors, saying to them, ‘Rejoice with me, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25586J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25586J\"></sup>I have found my sheep that was lost.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Just so, I tell you, there will be more joy in heaven over one sinner who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25587K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25587K\"></sup>repents than over ninety-nine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25587L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25587L\"></sup>righteous persons who need no repentance.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Or what woman, having ten silver coins, if she loses one coin, does not light a lamp and sweep the house and seek diligently until she finds it?</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when she has found it, she calls together her friends and neighbors, saying, ‘Rejoice with me, for I have found the coin that I had lost.’</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Just so, I tell you, there is joy before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25590M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25590M\"></sup>the angels of God over one sinner who repents.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“There was a man who had two sons.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And the younger of them said to his father, ‘Father, give me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25592N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25592N\"></sup>the share of property that is coming to me.’ And he divided <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25592O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25592O\"></sup>his property between them.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Not many days later, the younger son gathered all he had and took a journey into a far country, and there he squandered his property in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25593P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25593P\"></sup>reckless living.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And when he had spent everything, a severe famine arose in that country, and he began to be in need.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So he went and hired himself out to one of the citizens of that country, who sent him into his fields to feed pigs.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25596Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25596Q\"></sup>was longing to be fed with the pods that the pigs ate, and no one gave him anything.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25597R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25597R\"></sup>when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25597S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25597S\"></sup>came to himself, he said, ‘How many of my father's hired servants have more than enough bread, but I perish here with hunger!</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will arise and go to my father, and I will say to him, “Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25598T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25598T\"></sup>I have sinned against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25598U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25598U\"></sup>heaven and before you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25599V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25599V\"></sup>I am no longer worthy to be called your son. Treat me as one of your hired servants.”’</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he arose and came to his father. But while he was still a long way off, his father saw him and felt compassion, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25600W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25600W\"></sup>ran and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25600X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25600X\"></sup>embraced him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25600Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25600Y\"></sup>kissed him.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the son said to him, ‘Father, I have sinned against heaven and before you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25601Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25601Z\"></sup>I am no longer worthy to be called your son.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But the father said to his servants, ‘Bring quickly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25602AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25602AA\"></sup>the best robe, and put it on him, and put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25602AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25602AB\"></sup>a ring on his hand, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25602AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25602AC\"></sup>shoes on his feet.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25603AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25603AD\"></sup>the fattened calf and kill it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25603AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25603AE\"></sup>let us eat and celebrate.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For this my son <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25604AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25604AF\"></sup>was dead, and is alive again; he was lost, and is found.’ And they began to celebrate.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Now his older son was in the field, and as he came and drew near to the house, he heard music and dancing.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And he called one of the servants and asked what these things meant.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he said to him, ‘Your brother has come, and your father has killed the fattened calf, because he has received him back safe and sound.’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But he was angry and refused to go in. His father came out and entreated him,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>but he answered his father, ‘Look, these many years I have served you, and I never disobeyed your command, yet you never gave me a young goat, that I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25609AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25609AG\"></sup>celebrate with my friends.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But when this son of yours came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25610AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25610AH\"></sup>who has devoured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25610AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25610AI\"></sup>your property with prostitutes, you killed the fattened calf for him!’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And he said to him, ‘Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25611AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25611AJ\"></sup>you are always with me, and all that is mine is yours.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>It was fitting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25612AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25612AK\"></sup>to celebrate and be glad, for this your brother <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25612AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25612AL\"></sup>was dead, and is alive; he was lost, and is found.’”</span>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>He also said to the disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“There was a rich man who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25613A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25613A\"></sup>a manager, and charges were brought to him that this man was wasting his possessions.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he called him and said to him, ‘What is this that I hear about you? Turn in the account of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25614B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25614B\"></sup>management, for you can no longer be manager.’</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the manager said to himself, ‘What shall I do, since my master is taking the management away from me? I am not strong enough to dig, and I am ashamed to beg.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I have decided what to do, so that when I am removed from management, people may receive me into their houses.’</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So, summoning his master's debtors one by one, he said to the first, ‘How much do you owe my master?’</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said, ‘A hundred measures of oil.’ He said to him, ‘Take your bill, and sit down quickly and write fifty.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he said to another, ‘And how much do you owe?’ He said, ‘A hundred measures of wheat.’ He said to him, ‘Take your bill, and write eighty.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The master commended the dishonest manager for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25620C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25620C\"></sup>shrewdness. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25620D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25620D\"></sup>the sons of this world are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25620E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25620E\"></sup>more shrewd in dealing with their own generation than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25620F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25620F\"></sup>the sons of light.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25621G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25621G\"></sup>make friends for yourselves by means of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25621H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25621H\"></sup>unrighteous wealth, so that when it fails they may receive you into the eternal dwellings.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25622I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25622I\"></sup>“One who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25622J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25622J\"></sup>faithful in a very little is also faithful in much, and one who is dishonest in a very little is also dishonest in much.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If then you have not been faithful in the unrighteous wealth, who will entrust to you the true riches?</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And if you have not been faithful in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25624K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25624K\"></sup>that which is another's, who will give you that which is your own?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25625L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25625L\"></sup>No servant can serve two masters, for either he will hate the one and love the other, or he will be devoted to the one and despise the other. You cannot serve God and money.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25626M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25626M\"></sup>The Pharisees, who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25626N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25626N\"></sup>lovers of money, heard all these things, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25626O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25626O\"></sup>ridiculed him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You are those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25627P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25627P\"></sup>justify yourselves before men, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25627Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25627Q\"></sup>God knows your hearts. For what is exalted among men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25627R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25627R\"></sup>is an abomination in the sight of God.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25628S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25628S\"></sup>“The Law and the Prophets were until John; since then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25628T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25628T\"></sup>the good news of the kingdom of God is preached, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25628U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25628U\"></sup>everyone forces his way into it.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25629V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25629V\"></sup>it is easier for heaven and earth to pass away than for one dot of the Law to become void.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25630W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25630W\"></sup>“Everyone who divorces his wife and marries another commits adultery, and he who marries a woman divorced from her husband commits adultery.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“There was a rich man who was clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25631X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25631X\"></sup>purple and fine linen and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25631Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25631Y\"></sup>who feasted sumptuously every day.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And at his gate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25632Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25632Z\"></sup>was laid a poor man named Lazarus, covered with sores,</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>who desired to be fed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25633AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25633AA\"></sup>what fell from the rich man's table. Moreover, even the dogs came and licked his sores.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The poor man died and was carried by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25634AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25634AB\"></sup>the angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25634AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25634AC\"></sup>to Abraham's side. The rich man also died and was buried,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25635AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25635AD\"></sup>Hades, being in torment, he lifted up his eyes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25635AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25635AE\"></sup>saw Abraham far off and Lazarus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25635AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25635AF\"></sup>at his side.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he called out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25636AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25636AG\"></sup>‘Father Abraham, have mercy on me, and send Lazarus to dip the end of his finger in water and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25636AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25636AH\"></sup>cool my tongue, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25636AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25636AI\"></sup>I am in anguish in this flame.’</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But Abraham said, ‘Child, remember that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25637AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25637AJ\"></sup>you in your lifetime received your good things, and Lazarus in like manner bad things; but now he is comforted here, and you are in anguish.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And besides all this, between us and you a great chasm has been fixed, in order that those who would pass from here to you may not be able, and none may cross from there to us.’</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he said, ‘Then I beg you, father, to send him to my father's house—</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for I have five brothers—so that he may warn them, lest they also come into this place of torment.’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But Abraham said, ‘They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25641AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25641AK\"></sup>Moses and the Prophets; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25641AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25641AL\"></sup>let them hear them.’</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And he said, ‘No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25642AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25642AM\"></sup>father Abraham, but if someone goes to them from the dead, they will repent.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>He said to him, ‘If they do not hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25643AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25643AN\"></sup>Moses and the Prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25643AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25643AO\"></sup>neither will they be convinced if someone should rise from the dead.’”</span>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>And he said to his disciples, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25644A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25644A\"></sup>“Temptations to sin are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25644B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25644B\"></sup>sure to come, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25644C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25644C\"></sup>woe to the one through whom they come!</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25645D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25645D\"></sup>It would be better for him if a millstone were hung around his neck and he were cast into the sea than that he should cause one of these little ones to sin.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Pay attention to yourselves! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25646E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25646E\"></sup>If your brother sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25646F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25646F\"></sup>rebuke him, and if he repents, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25646G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25646G\"></sup>forgive him,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and if he sins against you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25647H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25647H\"></sup>seven times in the day, and turns to you seven times, saying, ‘I repent,’ you must forgive him.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25648I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25648I\"></sup>The apostles said to the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25648J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25648J\"></sup>“Increase our faith!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the Lord said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25649K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25649K\"></sup>“If you had faith like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25649L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25649L\"></sup>a grain of mustard seed, you could say to this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25649M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25649M\"></sup>mulberry tree, ‘Be uprooted and planted in the sea,’ and it would obey you.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Will any one of you who has a servant plowing or keeping sheep say to him when he has come in from the field, ‘Come at once and recline at table’?</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Will he not rather say to him, ‘Prepare supper for me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25651N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25651N\"></sup>dress properly, and serve me while I eat and drink, and afterward you will eat and drink’?</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Does he thank the servant because he did what was commanded?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So you also, when you have done all that you were commanded, say, ‘We are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25653O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25653O\"></sup>unworthy servants; we have only done what was our duty.’”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25654P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25654P\"></sup>On the way to Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25654Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25654Q\"></sup>he was passing along between Samaria and Galilee.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And as he entered a village, he was met by ten lepers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25655R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25655R\"></sup>who stood at a distance",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and lifted up their voices, saying, “Jesus, Master, have mercy on us.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When he saw them he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25657S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25657S\"></sup>show yourselves to the priests.”</span> And as they went they were cleansed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then one of them, when he saw that he was healed, turned back, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25658T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25658T\"></sup>praising God with a loud voice;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25659U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25659U\"></sup>he fell on his face at Jesus' feet, giving him thanks. Now he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25659V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25659V\"></sup>a Samaritan.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Were not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25660W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25660W\"></sup>ten cleansed? Where are the nine?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Was no one found to return and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25661X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25661X\"></sup>give praise to God except this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25661Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25661Y\"></sup>foreigner?”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Rise and go your way; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25662Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25662Z\"></sup>your faith has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25662AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25662AA\"></sup>made you well.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Being asked by the Pharisees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25663AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25663AB\"></sup>when the kingdom of God would come, he answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“The kingdom of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25663AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25663AC\"></sup>is not coming in ways that can be observed,</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25664AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25664AD\"></sup>will they say, ‘Look, here it is!’ or ‘There!’ for behold, the kingdom of God is in the midst of you.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And he said to the disciples, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25665AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25665AE\"></sup>“The days are coming when you will desire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25665AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25665AF\"></sup>to see one of the days of the Son of Man, and you will not see it.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25666AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25666AG\"></sup>And they will say to you, ‘Look, there!’ or ‘Look, here!’ Do not go out or follow them.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25667AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25667AH\"></sup>For as the lightning flashes and lights up the sky from one side to the other, so will the Son of Man be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25667AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25667AI\"></sup>in his day.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25668AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25668AJ\"></sup>he must suffer many things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25668AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25668AK\"></sup>be rejected by this generation.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25669AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25669AL\"></sup>Just as it was in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25669AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25669AM\"></sup>Noah, so will it be in the days of the Son of Man.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25670AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25670AN\"></sup>They were eating and drinking and marrying and being given in marriage, until the day when Noah entered the ark, and the flood came and destroyed them all.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Likewise, just as it was in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25671AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25671AO\"></sup>Lot—they were eating and drinking, buying and selling, planting and building,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25672AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25672AP\"></sup>but on the day when Lot went out from Sodom, fire and sulfur rained from heaven and destroyed them all—</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>so will it be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25673AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25673AQ\"></sup>on the day when the Son of Man is revealed.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>On that day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25674AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25674AR\"></sup>let the one who is on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25674AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25674AS\"></sup>the housetop, with his goods in the house, not come down to take them away, and likewise let the one who is in the field not turn back.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25675AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25675AT\"></sup>Remember Lot's wife.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25676AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25676AU\"></sup>Whoever seeks to preserve his life will lose it, but whoever loses his life will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25676AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25676AV\"></sup>keep it.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>I tell you, in that night there will be two in one bed. One will be taken and the other left.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25678AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25678AW\"></sup>There will be two women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25678AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25678AX\"></sup>grinding together. One will be taken and the other left.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And they said to him, “Where, Lord?” He said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25679AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25679AY\"></sup>“Where the corpse is, there the vultures will gather.”</span>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>And he told them a parable to the effect that they ought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25680A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25680A\"></sup>always to pray and not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25680B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25680B\"></sup>lose heart.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said, <span class=\"woj\">“In a certain city there was a judge who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25681C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25681C\"></sup>neither feared God nor respected man.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And there was a widow in that city who kept coming to him and saying, ‘Give me justice against my adversary.’</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For a while he refused, but afterward he said to himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25683D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25683D\"></sup>‘Though I neither fear God nor respect man,</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>yet because this widow keeps bothering me, I will give her justice, so that she will not beat me down by her continual coming.’”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the Lord said, <span class=\"woj\">“Hear what the unrighteous judge says.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25686E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25686E\"></sup>will not God give justice to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25686F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25686F\"></sup>his elect, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25686G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25686G\"></sup>who cry to him day and night? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25686H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25686H\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25686I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25686I\"></sup>Will he delay long over them?</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I tell you, he will give justice to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25687J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25687J\"></sup>speedily. Nevertheless, when the Son of Man comes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25687K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25687K\"></sup>will he find faith on earth?”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He also told this parable to some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25688L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25688L\"></sup>who trusted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25688M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25688M\"></sup>in themselves that they were righteous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25688N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25688N\"></sup>and treated others with contempt:",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Two men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25689O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25689O\"></sup>went up into the temple to pray, one a Pharisee and the other a tax collector.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The Pharisee, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25690P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25690P\"></sup>standing by himself, prayed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25690Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25690Q\"></sup>thus: ‘God, I thank you that I am not like other men, extortioners, unjust, adulterers, or even like this tax collector.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25691R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25691R\"></sup>I fast twice a week; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25691S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25691S\"></sup>I give tithes of all that I get.’</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But the tax collector, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25692T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25692T\"></sup>standing far off, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25692U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25692U\"></sup>would not even lift up his eyes to heaven, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25692V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25692V\"></sup>beat his breast, saying, ‘God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25692W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25692W\"></sup>be merciful to me, a sinner!’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I tell you, this man went down to his house justified, rather than the other. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25693X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25693X\"></sup>everyone who exalts himself will be humbled, but the one who humbles himself will be exalted.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25694Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25694Y\"></sup>Now they were bringing even infants to him that he might touch them. And when the disciples saw it, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25694Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25694Z\"></sup>rebuked them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Jesus called them to him, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25695AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25695AA\"></sup>“Let the children come to me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25695AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25695AB\"></sup>do not hinder them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25695AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25695AC\"></sup>for to such belongs the kingdom of God.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25696AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25696AD\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, whoever does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25696AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25696AE\"></sup>receive the kingdom of God like a child shall not enter it.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25697AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25697AF\"></sup>And a ruler asked him, “Good Teacher, what must I do to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25697AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25697AG\"></sup>inherit eternal life?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you call me good? No one is good except God alone.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You know the commandments: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25699AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25699AH\"></sup>‘Do not commit adultery, Do not murder, Do not steal, Do not bear false witness, Honor your father and mother.’”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25700AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25700AI\"></sup>“All these I have kept from my youth.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When Jesus heard this, he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“One thing you still lack. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25701AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25701AJ\"></sup>Sell all that you have and distribute to the poor, and you will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25701AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25701AK\"></sup>treasure in heaven; and come, follow me.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25702AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25702AL\"></sup>But when he heard these things, he became very sad, for he was extremely rich.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Jesus, seeing that he had become sad, said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25703AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25703AM\"></sup>“How difficult it is for those who have wealth to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25703AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25703AN\"></sup>the kingdom of God!</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For it is easier for a camel to go through the eye of a needle than for a rich person to enter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25704AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25704AO\"></sup>the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Those who heard it said, “Then who can be saved?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25706AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25706AP\"></sup>“What is impossible with man is possible with God.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And Peter said, “See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25707AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25707AQ\"></sup>we have left our homes and followed you.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25708AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25708AR\"></sup>there is no one who has left house or wife or brothers or parents or children, for the sake of the kingdom of God,</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>who will not receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25709AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25709AS\"></sup>many times more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25709AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25709AT\"></sup>in this time, and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25709AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25709AU\"></sup>the age to come eternal life.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25710AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25710AV\"></sup>And taking the twelve, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“See, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25710AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25710AW\"></sup>we are going up to Jerusalem, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25710AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25710AX\"></sup>everything that is written about the Son of Man by the prophets will be accomplished.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For he will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25711AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25711AY\"></sup>delivered over to the Gentiles and will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25711AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25711AZ\"></sup>mocked and shamefully treated and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25711BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25711BA\"></sup>spit upon.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And after flogging him, they will kill him, and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25712BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25712BB\"></sup>the third day he will rise.”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25713BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25713BC\"></sup>But they understood none of these things. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25713BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25713BD\"></sup>This saying was hidden from them, and they did not grasp what was said.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25714BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25714BE\"></sup>As he drew near to Jericho, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25714BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25714BF\"></sup>a blind man was sitting by the roadside begging.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And hearing a crowd going by, he inquired what this meant.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>They told him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25716BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25716BG\"></sup>“Jesus of Nazareth is passing by.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he cried out, “Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25717BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25717BH\"></sup>Son of David, have mercy on me!”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And those who were in front <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25718BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25718BI\"></sup>rebuked him, telling him to be silent. But he cried out all the more, “Son of David, have mercy on me!”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And Jesus stopped and commanded him to be brought to him. And when he came near, he asked him,",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25720BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25720BJ\"></sup>“What do you want me to do for you?”</span> He said, “Lord, let me recover my sight.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Recover your sight; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25721BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25721BK\"></sup>your faith has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25721BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25721BL\"></sup>made you well.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And immediately he recovered his sight and followed him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25722BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25722BM\"></sup>glorifying God. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25722BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25722BN\"></sup>all the people, when they saw it, gave praise to God."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25723A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25723A\"></sup>He entered Jericho and was passing through.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And behold, there was a man named Zacchaeus. He was a chief tax collector and was rich.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25725B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25725B\"></sup>he was seeking to see who Jesus was, but on account of the crowd he could not, because he was small in stature.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So he ran on ahead and climbed up into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25726C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25726C\"></sup>a sycamore tree to see him, for he was about to pass that way.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when Jesus came to the place, he looked up and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Zacchaeus, hurry and come down, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25727D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25727D\"></sup>I must stay at your house today.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So he hurried and came down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25728E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25728E\"></sup>received him joyfully.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when they saw it, they all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25729F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25729F\"></sup>grumbled, “He has gone in to be the guest of a man who is a sinner.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Zacchaeus stood and said to the Lord, “Behold, Lord, the half of my goods <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25730G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25730G\"></sup>I give to the poor. And if I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25730H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25730H\"></sup>defrauded anyone of anything, I restore it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25730I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25730I\"></sup>fourfold.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Today salvation has come to this house, since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25731J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25731J\"></sup>he also is a son of Abraham.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25732K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25732K\"></sup>the Son of Man came to seek and to save the lost.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As they heard these things, he proceeded to tell a parable, because he was near to Jerusalem, and because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25733L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25733L\"></sup>they supposed that the kingdom of God was to appear immediately.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He said therefore, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25734M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25734M\"></sup>“A nobleman went into a far country to receive for himself a kingdom and then return.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Calling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25735N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25735N\"></sup>ten of his servants, he gave them ten minas, and said to them, ‘Engage in business <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25735O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25735O\"></sup>until I come.’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25736P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25736P\"></sup>his citizens hated him and sent a delegation after him, saying, ‘We do not want this man to reign over us.’</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When he returned, having received the kingdom, he ordered these servants to whom he had given the money to be called to him, that he might know what they had gained by doing business.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The first came before him, saying, ‘Lord, your mina has made ten minas more.’</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And he said to him, ‘Well done, good servant! Because you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25739Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25739Q\"></sup>faithful in a very little, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25739R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25739R\"></sup>you shall have authority over ten cities.’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the second came, saying, ‘Lord, your mina has made five minas.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he said to him, ‘And you are to be over five cities.’</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then another came, saying, ‘Lord, here is your mina, which I kept laid away in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25742S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25742S\"></sup>a handkerchief;</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for I was afraid of you, because you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25743T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25743T\"></sup>a severe man. You take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25743U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25743U\"></sup>what you did not deposit, and reap what you did not sow.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25744V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25744V\"></sup>‘I will condemn you with your own words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25744W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25744W\"></sup>you wicked servant! You knew that I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25744X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25744X\"></sup>a severe man, taking what I did not deposit and reaping what I did not sow?</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Why then did you not put my money in the bank, and at my coming I might have collected it with interest?’</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And he said to those who stood by, ‘Take the mina from him, and give it to the one who has the ten minas.’</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And they said to him, ‘Lord, he has ten minas!’</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>‘I tell you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25748Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25748Y\"></sup>to everyone who has, more will be given, but from the one who has not, even what he has will be taken away.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25749Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25749Z\"></sup>as for these enemies of mine, who did not want me to reign over them, bring them here and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25749AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25749AA\"></sup>slaughter them before me.’”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And when he had said these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25750AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25750AB\"></sup>he went on ahead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25750AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25750AC\"></sup>going up to Jerusalem.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25751AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25751AD\"></sup>When he drew near to Bethphage and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25751AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25751AE\"></sup>Bethany, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25751AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25751AF\"></sup>the mount that is called Olivet, he sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25751AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25751AG\"></sup>two of the disciples,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the village in front of you, where on entering you will find a colt tied, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25752AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25752AH\"></sup>on which no one has ever yet sat. Untie it and bring it here.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>If anyone asks you, ‘Why are you untying it?’ you shall say this: ‘The Lord has need of it.’”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So those who were sent went away and found it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25754AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25754AI\"></sup>just as he had told them.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And as they were untying the colt, its owners said to them, “Why are you untying the colt?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And they said, “The Lord has need of it.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And they brought it to Jesus, and throwing their cloaks on the colt, they set Jesus on it.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And as he rode along, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25758AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25758AJ\"></sup>spread their cloaks on the road.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>As he was drawing near—already on the way down the Mount of Olives—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25759AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25759AK\"></sup>the whole multitude of his disciples began to rejoice and praise God with a loud voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25759AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25759AL\"></sup>for all the mighty works that they had seen,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25760AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25760AM\"></sup>“Blessed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25760AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25760AN\"></sup>the King who comes in the name of the Lord! Peace in heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25760AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25760AO\"></sup>glory in the highest!”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25761AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25761AP\"></sup>And some of the Pharisees in the crowd said to him, “Teacher, rebuke your disciples.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>He answered, <span class=\"woj\">“I tell you, if these were silent, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25762AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25762AQ\"></sup>the very stones would cry out.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25763AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25763AR\"></sup>And when he drew near and saw the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25763AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25763AS\"></sup>he wept over it,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25764AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25764AT\"></sup>“Would that you, even you, had known on this day the things that make for peace! But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25764AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25764AU\"></sup>they are hidden from your eyes.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25765AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25765AV\"></sup>the days will come upon you, when your enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25765AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25765AW\"></sup>will set up a barricade around you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25765AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25765AX\"></sup>surround you and hem you in on every side</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25766AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25766AY\"></sup>and tear you down to the ground, you and your children within you. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25766AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25766AZ\"></sup>they will not leave one stone upon another in you, because you did not know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25766BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25766BA\"></sup>the time of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25766BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25766BB\"></sup>visitation.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25767BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25767BC\"></sup>And he entered the temple and began to drive out those who sold,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25768BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25768BD\"></sup>‘My house shall be a house of prayer,’ but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25768BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25768BE\"></sup>you have made it a den of robbers.”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25769BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25769BF\"></sup>And he was teaching daily in the temple. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25769BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25769BG\"></sup>The chief priests and the scribes and the principal men of the people were seeking to destroy him,",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>but they did not find anything they could do, for all the people were hanging on his words."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25771A\"></sup>One day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25771B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25771B\"></sup>as Jesus was teaching the people in the temple and preaching the gospel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25771C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25771C\"></sup>the chief priests and the scribes with the elders came up",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and said to him, “Tell us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25772D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25772D\"></sup>by what authority you do these things, or who it is that gave you this authority.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I also will ask you a question. Now tell me,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>was the baptism of John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25774E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25774E\"></sup>from heaven or from man?”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And they discussed it with one another, saying, “If we say, ‘From heaven,’ he will say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25775F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25775F\"></sup>‘Why did you not believe him?’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But if we say, ‘From man,’ all the people will stone us to death, for they are convinced that John was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25776G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25776G\"></sup>a prophet.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So they answered that they did not know where it came from.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Neither will I tell you by what authority I do these things.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25779H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25779H\"></sup>And he began to tell the people this parable: <span class=\"woj\">“A man planted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25779I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25779I\"></sup>a vineyard and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25779J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25779J\"></sup>let it out to tenants and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25779K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25779K\"></sup>went into another country for a long while.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When the time came, he sent a servant to the tenants, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25780L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25780L\"></sup>they would give him some of the fruit of the vineyard. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25780M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25780M\"></sup>But the tenants beat him and sent him away empty-handed.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25781N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25781N\"></sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25781O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25781O\"></sup>he sent another servant. But they also beat and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25781P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25781P\"></sup>treated him shamefully, and sent him away empty-handed.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25782Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25782Q\"></sup>And he sent yet a third. This one also they wounded and cast out.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the owner of the vineyard said, ‘What shall I do? I will send my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25783R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25783R\"></sup>beloved son; perhaps they will respect him.’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when the tenants saw him, they said to themselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25784S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25784S\"></sup>‘This is the heir. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25784T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25784T\"></sup>Let us kill him, so that the inheritance may be ours.’</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25785U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25785U\"></sup>threw him out of the vineyard and killed him. What then will the owner of the vineyard do to them?</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25786V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25786V\"></sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25786W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25786W\"></sup>come and destroy those tenants and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25786X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25786X\"></sup>give the vineyard to others.”</span> When they heard this, they said, “Surely not!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25787Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25787Y\"></sup>looked directly at them and said, <span class=\"woj\">“What then is this that is written:</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25787Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25787Z\"></sup>“‘The stone that the builders rejected</span><span class=\"woj\">has become the cornerstone’?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25788AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25788AA\"></sup>Everyone who falls on that stone will be broken to pieces, and when it falls <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25788AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25788AB\"></sup>on anyone, it will crush him.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25789AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25789AC\"></sup>The scribes and the chief priests sought to lay hands on him at that very hour, for they perceived that he had told this parable against them, but they feared the people.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25790AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25790AD\"></sup>So they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25790AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25790AE\"></sup>watched him and sent spies, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25790AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25790AF\"></sup>pretended to be sincere, that they might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25790AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25790AG\"></sup>catch him in something he said, so as to deliver him up to the authority and jurisdiction of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25790AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25790AH\"></sup>the governor.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So they asked him, “Teacher, we know that you speak and teach rightly, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25791AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25791AI\"></sup>show no partiality, but truly teach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25791AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25791AJ\"></sup>the way of God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Is it lawful for us to give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25792AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25792AK\"></sup>tribute to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25792AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25792AL\"></sup>Caesar, or not?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But he perceived their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25793AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25793AM\"></sup>craftiness, and said to them,",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Show me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25794AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25794AN\"></sup>a denarius. Whose likeness and inscription does it have?”</span> They said, “Caesar's.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25795AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25795AO\"></sup>render to Caesar the things that are Caesar's, and to God the things that are God's.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And they were not able in the presence of the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25796AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25796AP\"></sup>to catch him in what he said, but marveling at his answer they became silent.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>There came to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25797AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25797AQ\"></sup>some Sadducees, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25797AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25797AR\"></sup>those who deny that there is a resurrection,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and they asked him a question, saying, “Teacher, Moses wrote for us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25798AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25798AS\"></sup>that if a man's brother dies, having a wife but no children, the man must take the widow and raise up offspring for his brother.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Now there were seven brothers. The first took a wife, and died without children.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And the second",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and the third took her, and likewise all seven left no children and died.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Afterward the woman also died.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>In the resurrection, therefore, whose wife will the woman be? For the seven had her as wife.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25804AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25804AT\"></sup>“The sons of this age <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25804AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25804AU\"></sup>marry and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25804AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25804AV\"></sup>are given in marriage,</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>but those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25805AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25805AW\"></sup>considered worthy to attain to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25805AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25805AX\"></sup>that age and to the resurrection from the dead <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25805AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25805AY\"></sup>neither marry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25805AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25805AZ\"></sup>nor are given in marriage,</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25806BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25806BA\"></sup>they cannot die anymore, because they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25806BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25806BB\"></sup>equal to angels and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25806BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25806BC\"></sup>are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25806BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25806BD\"></sup>sons of God, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25806BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25806BE\"></sup>sons of the resurrection.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But that the dead are raised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25807BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25807BF\"></sup>even Moses showed, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25807BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25807BG\"></sup>the passage about the bush, where he calls <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25807BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25807BH\"></sup>the Lord the God of Abraham and the God of Isaac and the God of Jacob.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Now he is not God of the dead, but of the living, for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25808BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25808BI\"></sup>live to him.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Then some of the scribes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25809BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25809BJ\"></sup>answered, “Teacher, you have spoken well.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25810BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25810BK\"></sup>they no longer dared to ask him any question.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25811BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25811BL\"></sup>But he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“How can they say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25811BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25811BM\"></sup>the Christ is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25811BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25811BN\"></sup>David's son?</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>For David himself says in the Book of Psalms,</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25812BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25812BO\"></sup>“‘The Lord said to my Lord,</span><span class=\"woj\">“Sit at my right hand,</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>until I make your enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25813BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25813BP\"></sup>your footstool.”’</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>David thus calls him Lord, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25814BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25814BQ\"></sup>how is he his son?”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25815BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25815BR\"></sup>And in the hearing of all the people he said to his disciples,",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>“Beware of the scribes, who like to walk around in long robes, and love greetings in the marketplaces and the best seats in the synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25816BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25816BS\"></sup>the places of honor at feasts,</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25817BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25817BT\"></sup>who devour widows' houses and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25817BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25817BU\"></sup>for a pretense make long prayers. They will receive the greater condemnation.”</span>"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25818A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25818A\"></sup>Jesus looked up and saw the rich <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25818B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25818B\"></sup>putting their gifts into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25818C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25818C\"></sup>the offering box,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and he saw a poor widow put in two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25819D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25819D\"></sup>small copper coins.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I tell you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25820E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25820E\"></sup>this poor widow has put in more than all of them.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For they all contributed out of their abundance, but she out of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25821F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25821F\"></sup>poverty put in all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25821G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25821G\"></sup>she had to live on.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25822H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25822H\"></sup>And while some were speaking of the temple, how it was adorned with noble stones and offerings, he said,",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“As for these things that you see, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25823I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25823I\"></sup>the days will come when there will not be left here one stone upon another that will not be thrown down.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And they asked him, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25824J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25824J\"></sup>when will these things be, and what will be the sign when these things are about to take place?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25825K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25825K\"></sup>“See that you are not led astray. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25825L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25825L\"></sup>many will come in my name, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25825M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25825M\"></sup>‘I am he!’ and, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25825N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25825N\"></sup>‘The time is at hand!’ Do not go after them.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when you hear of wars and tumults, do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25826O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25826O\"></sup>terrified, for these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25826P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25826P\"></sup>must first take place, but the end will not be at once.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25827Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25827Q\"></sup>“Nation will rise against nation, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25827R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25827R\"></sup>kingdom against kingdom.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There will be great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25828S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25828S\"></sup>earthquakes, and in various places <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25828T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25828T\"></sup>famines and pestilences. And there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25828U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25828U\"></sup>terrors and great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25828V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25828V\"></sup>signs from heaven.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But before all this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25829W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25829W\"></sup>they will lay their hands on you and persecute you, delivering you up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25829X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25829X\"></sup>the synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25829Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25829Y\"></sup>prisons, and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25829Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25829Z\"></sup>will be brought before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25829AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25829AA\"></sup>kings and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25829AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25829AB\"></sup>governors for my name's sake.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25830AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25830AC\"></sup>This will be your opportunity to bear witness.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Settle it therefore in your minds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25831AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25831AD\"></sup>not to meditate beforehand how to answer,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25832AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25832AE\"></sup>I will give you a mouth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25832AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25832AF\"></sup>wisdom, which none of your adversaries will be able to withstand or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25832AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25832AG\"></sup>contradict.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will be delivered up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25833AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25833AH\"></sup>even by parents and brothers and relatives and friends, and some of you they will put to death.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25834AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25834AI\"></sup>You will be hated by all for my name's sake.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25835AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25835AJ\"></sup>not a hair of your head will perish.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>By your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25836AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25836AK\"></sup>endurance you will gain your lives.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25837AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25837AL\"></sup>when you see Jerusalem surrounded by armies, then know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25837AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25837AM\"></sup>its desolation has come near.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then let those who are in Judea flee to the mountains, and let those who are inside the city depart, and let not those who are out in the country enter it,</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for these are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25839AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25839AN\"></sup>days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25839AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25839AO\"></sup>vengeance, to fulfill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25839AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25839AP\"></sup>all that is written.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25840AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25840AQ\"></sup>Alas for women who are pregnant and for those who are nursing infants in those days! For there will be great distress upon the earth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25840AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25840AR\"></sup>wrath against this people.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They will fall by the edge of the sword and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25841AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25841AS\"></sup>be led captive among all nations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25841AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25841AT\"></sup>Jerusalem will be trampled underfoot by the Gentiles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25841AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25841AU\"></sup>until the times of the Gentiles are fulfilled.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25842AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25842AV\"></sup>there will be signs in sun and moon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25842AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25842AW\"></sup>and stars, and on the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25842AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25842AX\"></sup>distress of nations in perplexity because of the roaring of the sea and the waves,</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>people fainting with fear and with foreboding of what is coming on the world. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25843AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25843AY\"></sup>the powers of the heavens will be shaken.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And then they will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25844AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25844AZ\"></sup>the Son of Man coming in a cloud <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25844BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25844BA\"></sup>with power and great glory.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Now when these things begin to take place, straighten up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25845BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25845BB\"></sup>raise your heads, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25845BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25845BC\"></sup>your redemption is drawing near.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he told them a parable: <span class=\"woj\">“Look at the fig tree, and all the trees.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>As soon as they come out in leaf, you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25847BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25847BD\"></sup>for yourselves and know that the summer is already near.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So also, when you see these things taking place, you know that the kingdom of God is near.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25849BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25849BE\"></sup>Truly, I say to you, this generation will not pass away until all has taken place.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25850BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25850BF\"></sup>Heaven and earth will pass away, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25850BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25850BG\"></sup>my words will not pass away.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“But watch yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25851BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25851BH\"></sup>lest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25851BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25851BI\"></sup>your hearts be weighed down with dissipation and drunkenness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25851BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25851BJ\"></sup>cares of this life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25851BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25851BK\"></sup>that day come upon you suddenly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25851BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25851BL\"></sup>like a trap.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For it will come upon all who dwell on the face of the whole earth.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25853BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25853BM\"></sup>stay awake at all times, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25853BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25853BN\"></sup>praying that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25853BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25853BO\"></sup>have strength to escape all these things that are going to take place, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25853BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25853BP\"></sup>to stand before the Son of Man.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25854BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25854BQ\"></sup>every day he was teaching in the temple, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25854BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25854BR\"></sup>at night he went out and lodged on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25854BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25854BS\"></sup>the mount called Olivet.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And early in the morning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25855BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25855BT\"></sup>all the people came to him in the temple to hear him."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25856A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25856A\"></sup>Now the Feast of Unleavened Bread drew near, which is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25856B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25856B\"></sup>the Passover.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the chief priests and the scribes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25857C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25857C\"></sup>were seeking how to put him to death, for they feared the people.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25858D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25858D\"></sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25858E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25858E\"></sup>Satan entered into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25858F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25858F\"></sup>Judas called Iscariot, who was of the number of the twelve.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He went away and conferred with the chief priests and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25859G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25859G\"></sup>officers how he might betray him to them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And they were glad, and agreed to give him money.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So he consented and sought an opportunity to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25861H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25861H\"></sup>betray him to them in the absence of a crowd.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25862I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25862I\"></sup>Then came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25862J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25862J\"></sup>the day of Unleavened Bread, on which the Passover lamb had to be sacrificed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So Jesus sent Peter and John, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Go and prepare the Passover for us, that we may eat it.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They said to him, “Where will you have us prepare it?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, when you have entered the city, a man carrying a jar of water will meet you. Follow him into the house that he enters</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and tell the master of the house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25866K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25866K\"></sup>‘The Teacher says to you, Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25866L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25866L\"></sup>the guest room, where I may eat the Passover with my disciples?’</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And he will show you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25867M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25867M\"></sup>a large upper room furnished; prepare it there.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And they went and found it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25868N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25868N\"></sup>just as he had told them, and they prepared the Passover.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25869O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25869O\"></sup>And when the hour came, he reclined at table, and the apostles with him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I have earnestly desired to eat this Passover with you before I suffer.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For I tell you I will not eat it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25871P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25871P\"></sup>until it is fulfilled in the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And he took a cup, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25872Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25872Q\"></sup>when he had given thanks he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Take this, and divide it among yourselves.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25873R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25873R\"></sup>For I tell you that from now on I will not drink of the fruit of the vine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25873S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25873S\"></sup>until the kingdom of God comes.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25874T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25874T\"></sup>And he took bread, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25874U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25874U\"></sup>when he had given thanks, he broke it and gave it to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25874V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25874V\"></sup>“This is my body, which is given for you. Do this in remembrance of me.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And likewise the cup after they had eaten, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25875W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25875W\"></sup>“This cup that is poured out for you is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25875X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25875X\"></sup>the new <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25875Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25875Y\"></sup>covenant in my blood.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25876Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25876Z\"></sup>But behold, the hand of him who betrays me is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25876AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25876AA\"></sup>with me on the table.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For the Son of Man goes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25877AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25877AB\"></sup>as it has been determined, but woe to that man by whom he is betrayed!”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And they began to question one another, which of them it could be who was going to do this.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25879AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25879AC\"></sup>A dispute also arose among them, as to which of them was to be regarded as the greatest.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25880AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25880AD\"></sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“The kings of the Gentiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25880AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25880AE\"></sup>exercise lordship over them, and those in authority over them are called benefactors.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25881AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25881AF\"></sup>But not so with you. Rather, let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25881AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25881AG\"></sup>the greatest among you become as the youngest, and the leader as one who serves.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For who is the greater, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25882AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25882AH\"></sup>one who reclines at table or one who serves? Is it not the one who reclines at table? But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25882AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25882AI\"></sup>I am among you as the one who serves.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“You are those who have stayed with me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25883AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25883AJ\"></sup>in my trials,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25884AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25884AK\"></sup>I assign to you, as my Father assigned to me, a kingdom,</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25885AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25885AL\"></sup>that you may eat and drink at my table in my kingdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25885AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25885AM\"></sup>sit on thrones judging <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25885AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25885AN\"></sup>the twelve tribes of Israel.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Simon, Simon, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25886AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25886AO\"></sup>Satan demanded to have you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25886AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25886AP\"></sup>that he might sift you like wheat,</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25887AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25887AQ\"></sup>I have prayed for you that your faith may not fail. And when you have turned again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25887AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25887AR\"></sup>strengthen your brothers.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Peter said to him, “Lord, I am ready to go with you both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25888AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25888AS\"></sup>to prison and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25888AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25888AT\"></sup>to death.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25889AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25889AU\"></sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“I tell you, Peter, the rooster will not crow this day, until you deny three times that you know me.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25890AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25890AV\"></sup>“When I sent you out with no moneybag or knapsack or sandals, did you lack anything?”</span> They said, “Nothing.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“But now let the one who has a moneybag take it, and likewise a knapsack. And let the one who has no sword sell his cloak and buy one.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For I tell you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25892AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25892AW\"></sup>this Scripture must be fulfilled in me: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25892AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25892AX\"></sup>‘And he was numbered with the transgressors.’ For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25892AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25892AY\"></sup>what is written about me has its fulfillment.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And they said, “Look, Lord, here are two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25893AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25893AZ\"></sup>swords.” And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25893BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25893BA\"></sup>“It is enough.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25894BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25894BB\"></sup>And he came out and went, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25894BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25894BC\"></sup>as was his custom, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25894BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25894BD\"></sup>the Mount of Olives, and the disciples followed him.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25895BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25895BE\"></sup>And when he came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25895BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25895BF\"></sup>the place, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25895BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25895BG\"></sup>“Pray that you may not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25895BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25895BH\"></sup>enter into temptation.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And he withdrew from them about a stone's throw, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25896BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25896BI\"></sup>knelt down and prayed,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25897BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25897BJ\"></sup>“Father, if you are willing, remove <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25897BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25897BK\"></sup>this cup from me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25897BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25897BL\"></sup>Nevertheless, not my will, but yours, be done.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And there appeared to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25898BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25898BM\"></sup>an angel from heaven, strengthening him.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25899BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25899BN\"></sup>being in agony he prayed more earnestly; and his sweat became like great drops of blood falling down to the ground.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And when he rose from prayer, he came to the disciples and found them sleeping for sorrow,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>and he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you sleeping? Rise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25901BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25901BO\"></sup>pray that you may not enter into temptation.”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25902BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25902BP\"></sup>While he was still speaking, there came a crowd, and the man called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25902BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25902BQ\"></sup>Judas, one of the twelve, was leading them. He drew near to Jesus to kiss him,",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>but Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Judas, would you betray the Son of Man with a kiss?”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And when those who were around him saw what would follow, they said, “Lord, shall we strike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25904BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25904BR\"></sup>with the sword?”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And one of them struck the servant of the high priest and cut off his right ear.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>But Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“No more of this!”</span> And he touched his ear and healed him.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Then Jesus said to the chief priests and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25907BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25907BS\"></sup>officers of the temple and elders, who had come out against him, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you come out as against a robber, with swords and clubs?</span>",
			"53": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25908BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25908BT\"></sup>I was with you day after day in the temple, you did not lay hands on me. But this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25908BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25908BU\"></sup>your hour, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25908BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25908BV\"></sup>the power of darkness.”</span>",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25909BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25909BW\"></sup>Then they seized him and led him away, bringing him into the high priest's house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25909BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25909BX\"></sup>and Peter was following at a distance.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25910BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25910BY\"></sup>And when they had kindled a fire in the middle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25910BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25910BZ\"></sup>the courtyard and sat down together, Peter sat down among them.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>Then a servant girl, seeing him as he sat in the light and looking closely at him, said, “This man also was with him.”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>But he denied it, saying, “Woman, I do not know him.”",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>And a little later someone else saw him and said, “You also are one of them.” But Peter said, “Man, I am not.”",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>And after an interval of about an hour still another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25914CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25914CA\"></sup>insisted, saying, “Certainly this man also was with him, for he too is a Galilean.”",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>But Peter said, “Man, I do not know what you are talking about.” And immediately, while he was still speaking, the rooster crowed.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>And the Lord turned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25916CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25916CB\"></sup>looked at Peter. And Peter remembered the saying of the Lord, how he had said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25916CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25916CC\"></sup>“Before the rooster crows today, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25916CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25916CD\"></sup>deny me three times.”</span>",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>And he went out and wept bitterly.",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25918CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25918CE\"></sup>Now the men who were holding Jesus in custody were mocking him as they beat him.",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25919CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25919CF\"></sup>They also blindfolded him and kept asking him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25919CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25919CG\"></sup>“Prophesy! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25919CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25919CH\"></sup>Who is it that struck you?”",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>And they said many other things against him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25920CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25920CI\"></sup>blaspheming him.",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25921CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25921CJ\"></sup>When day came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25921CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25921CK\"></sup>the assembly of the elders of the people gathered together, both chief priests and scribes. And they led him away to their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25921CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25921CL\"></sup>council, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25921CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25921CM\"></sup>said,",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25922CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25922CN\"></sup>“If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25922CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25922CO\"></sup>the Christ, tell us.” But he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“If I tell you, you will not believe,</span>",
			"68": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup>and if I ask you, you will not answer.</span>",
			"69": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup>But from now on the Son of Man shall be seated <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25924CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25924CP\"></sup>at the right hand of the power of God.”</span>",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup>So they all said, “Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25925CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25925CQ\"></sup>the Son of God, then?” And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25925CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25925CR\"></sup>“You say that I am.”</span>",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup>Then they said, “What further testimony do we need? We have heard it ourselves from his own lips.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25927A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25927A\"></sup>Then the whole company of them arose and brought him before Pilate.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And they began to accuse him, saying, “We found this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25928B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25928B\"></sup>misleading our nation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25928C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25928C\"></sup>forbidding us to give tribute to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25928D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25928D\"></sup>Caesar, and saying that he himself is Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25928E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25928E\"></sup>a king.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25929F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25929F\"></sup>And Pilate asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25929G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25929G\"></sup>“Are you the King of the Jews?” And he answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25929H\"></sup>“You have said so.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then Pilate said to the chief priests and the crowds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25930I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25930I\"></sup>“I find no guilt in this man.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they were urgent, saying, “He stirs up the people, teaching throughout all Judea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25931J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25931J\"></sup>from Galilee even to this place.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When Pilate heard this, he asked whether the man was a Galilean.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when he learned that he belonged to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25933K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25933K\"></sup>Herod's jurisdiction, he sent him over to Herod, who was himself in Jerusalem at that time.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When Herod saw Jesus, he was very glad, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25934L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25934L\"></sup>for he had long desired to see him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25934M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25934M\"></sup>because he had heard about him, and he was hoping <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25934N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25934N\"></sup>to see some sign done by him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So he questioned him at some length, but he made no answer.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The chief priests and the scribes stood by, vehemently accusing him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And Herod with his soldiers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25937O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25937O\"></sup>treated him with contempt and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25937P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25937P\"></sup>mocked him. Then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25937Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25937Q\"></sup>arraying him in splendid clothing, he sent him back to Pilate.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25938R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25938R\"></sup>Herod and Pilate became friends with each other that very day, for before this they had been at enmity with each other.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Pilate then called together the chief priests and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25939S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25939S\"></sup>the rulers and the people,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and said to them, “You brought me this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25940T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25940T\"></sup>as one who was misleading the people. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25940U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25940U\"></sup>after examining him before you, behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25940V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25940V\"></sup>did not find this man guilty of any of your charges against him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Neither did Herod, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25941W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25941W\"></sup>he sent him back to us. Look, nothing deserving death has been done by him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25942X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25942X\"></sup>I will therefore punish and release him.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25943Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25943Y\"></sup>But they all cried out together, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25943Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25943Z\"></sup>“Away with this man, and release to us Barabbas”—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>a man who had been thrown into prison for an insurrection started in the city and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25944AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25944AA\"></sup>for murder.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Pilate addressed them once more, desiring to release Jesus,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>but they kept shouting, “Crucify, crucify him!”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A third time he said to them, “Why? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25947AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25947AB\"></sup>What evil has he done? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25947AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25947AC\"></sup>I have found in him no guilt deserving death. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25947AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25947AD\"></sup>I will therefore punish and release him.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But they were urgent, demanding with loud cries that he should be crucified. And their voices prevailed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So Pilate decided that their demand should be granted.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He released the man who had been thrown into prison <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25950AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25950AE\"></sup>for insurrection and murder, for whom they asked, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25950AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25950AF\"></sup>but he delivered Jesus over to their will.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25951AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25951AG\"></sup>And as they led him away, they seized one Simon of Cyrene, who was coming in from the country, and laid on him the cross, to carry it behind Jesus.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And there followed him a great multitude of the people and of women who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25952AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25952AH\"></sup>mourning and lamenting for him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But turning to them Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Daughters of Jerusalem, do not weep for me, but weep for yourselves and for your children.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25954AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25954AI\"></sup>the days are coming when they will say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25954AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25954AJ\"></sup>‘Blessed are the barren and the wombs that never bore and the breasts that never nursed!’</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25955AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25955AK\"></sup>Then they will begin to say to the mountains, ‘Fall on us,’ and to the hills, ‘Cover us.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25956AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25956AL\"></sup>if they do these things when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25956AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25956AM\"></sup>the wood is green, what will happen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25956AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25956AN\"></sup>when it is dry?”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25957AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25957AO\"></sup>Two others, who were criminals, were led away to be put to death with him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25958AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25958AP\"></sup>And when they came to the place that is called The Skull, there they crucified him, and the criminals, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25958AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25958AQ\"></sup>one on his right and one on his left.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25959AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25959AR\"></sup>forgive them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25959AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25959AS\"></sup>for they know not what they do.”</span> And they cast lots <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25959AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25959AT\"></sup>to divide his garments.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960AU\"></sup>the people stood by, watching, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960AV\"></sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960AW\"></sup>the rulers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960AX\"></sup>scoffed at him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960AY\"></sup>“He saved others; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960AZ\"></sup>let him save himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960BA\"></sup>if he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960BB\"></sup>the Christ of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25960BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25960BC\"></sup>his Chosen One!”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>The soldiers also mocked him, coming up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25961BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25961BD\"></sup>offering him sour wine",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>and saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25962BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25962BE\"></sup>“If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25962BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25962BF\"></sup>the King of the Jews, save yourself!”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25963BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25963BG\"></sup>There was also an inscription over him, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25963BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25963BH\"></sup>the King of the Jews.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25964BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25964BI\"></sup>One of the criminals who were hanged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25964BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25964BJ\"></sup>railed at him, saying, “Are you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25964BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25964BK\"></sup>the Christ? Save yourself and us!”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But the other rebuked him, saying, “Do you not fear God, since you are under the same sentence of condemnation?",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And we indeed justly, for we are receiving the due reward of our deeds; but this man has done nothing wrong.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And he said, “Jesus, remember me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25967BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25967BL\"></sup>when you come into your kingdom.”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, I say to you, today you will be with me in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25968BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25968BM\"></sup>paradise.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25969BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25969BN\"></sup>It was now about the sixth hour, and there was darkness over the whole land until the ninth hour,",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>while the sun's light failed. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25970BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25970BO\"></sup>the curtain of the temple was torn in two.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Then Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25971BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25971BP\"></sup>calling out with a loud voice, said, <span class=\"woj\">“Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25971BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25971BQ\"></sup>into your hands I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25971BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25971BR\"></sup>commit my spirit!”</span> And having said this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25971BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25971BS\"></sup>he breathed his last.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25972BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25972BT\"></sup>when the centurion saw what had taken place, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25972BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25972BU\"></sup>he praised God, saying, “Certainly this man was innocent!”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And all the crowds that had assembled for this spectacle, when they saw what had taken place, returned home <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25973BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25973BV\"></sup>beating their breasts.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25974BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25974BW\"></sup>his acquaintances and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25974BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25974BX\"></sup>the women who had followed him from Galilee <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25974BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25974BY\"></sup>stood at a distance watching these things.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25975BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25975BZ\"></sup>Now there was a man named Joseph, from the Jewish town of Arimathea. He was a member of the council, a good and righteous man,",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>who had not consented to their decision and action; and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25976CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25976CA\"></sup>was looking for the kingdom of God.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>This man went to Pilate and asked for the body of Jesus.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>Then he took it down and wrapped it in a linen shroud and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25978CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25978CB\"></sup>laid him in a tomb cut in stone, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25978CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25978CC\"></sup>where no one had ever yet been laid.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>It was the day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25979CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25979CD\"></sup>Preparation, and the Sabbath was beginning.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25980CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25980CE\"></sup>The women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25980CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25980CF\"></sup>who had come with him from Galilee followed and saw the tomb and how his body was laid.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>Then they returned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25981CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25981CG\"></sup>prepared spices and ointments.On the Sabbath they rested <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25981CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25981CH\"></sup>according to the commandment."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25982A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25982A\"></sup>But on the first day of the week, at early dawn, they went to the tomb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25982B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25982B\"></sup>taking the spices they had prepared.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And they found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25983C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25983C\"></sup>the stone rolled away from the tomb,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>but when they went in they did not find the body of the Lord Jesus.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>While they were perplexed about this, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25985D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25985D\"></sup>two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25985E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25985E\"></sup>men stood by them in dazzling apparel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And as they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25986F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25986F\"></sup>frightened and bowed their faces to the ground, the men said to them, “Why do you seek the living among the dead?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He is not here, but has risen. Remember how he told you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25987G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25987G\"></sup>while he was still in Galilee,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25988H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25988H\"></sup>that the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25988I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25988I\"></sup>must be delivered into the hands of sinful men and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25988J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25988J\"></sup>be crucified and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25988K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25988K\"></sup>the third day rise.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25989L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25989L\"></sup>they remembered his words,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and returning from the tomb they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25990M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25990M\"></sup>told all these things to the eleven and to all the rest.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25991N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25991N\"></sup>Mary Magdalene and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25991O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25991O\"></sup>Joanna and Mary the mother of James and the other women with them who told these things to the apostles,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>but these words seemed to them an idle tale, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25992P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25992P\"></sup>they did not believe them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25993Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25993Q\"></sup>Peter rose and ran to the tomb; stooping and looking in, he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25993R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25993R\"></sup>the linen cloths by themselves; and he went home marveling at what had happened.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>That very day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25994S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25994S\"></sup>two of them were going to a village named Emmaus, about seven miles from Jerusalem,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and they were talking with each other about all these things that had happened.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>While they were talking and discussing together, Jesus himself drew near and went with them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-25997T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-25997T\"></sup>But their eyes were kept from recognizing him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“What is this conversation that you are holding with each other as you walk?”</span> And they stood still, looking sad.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then one of them, named Cleopas, answered him, “Are you the only visitor to Jerusalem who does not know the things that have happened there in these days?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“What things?”</span> And they said to him, “Concerning Jesus of Nazareth, a man who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26000U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26000U\"></sup>a prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26000V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26000V\"></sup>mighty in deed and word before God and all the people,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26001W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26001W\"></sup>how our chief priests and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26001X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26001X\"></sup>rulers delivered him up to be condemned to death, and crucified him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But we had hoped that he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26002Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26002Y\"></sup>the one to redeem Israel. Yes, and besides all this, it is now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26002Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26002Z\"></sup>the third day since these things happened.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Moreover, some women of our company amazed us. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26003AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26003AA\"></sup>They were at the tomb early in the morning,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26004AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26004AB\"></sup>when they did not find his body, they came back saying that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26004AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26004AC\"></sup>they had even seen a vision of angels, who said that he was alive.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26005AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26005AD\"></sup>Some of those who were with us went to the tomb and found it just as the women had said, but him they did not see.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“O foolish ones, and slow of heart to believe all that the prophets have spoken!</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26007AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26007AE\"></sup>Was it not necessary that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26007AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26007AF\"></sup>the Christ should suffer these things and enter into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26007AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26007AG\"></sup>his glory?”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26008AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26008AH\"></sup>beginning with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26008AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26008AI\"></sup>Moses and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26008AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26008AJ\"></sup>all the Prophets, he interpreted to them in all the Scriptures the things concerning himself.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So they drew near to the village to which they were going. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26009AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26009AK\"></sup>He acted as if he were going farther,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>but they urged him strongly, saying, “Stay with us, for it is toward evening and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26010AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26010AL\"></sup>the day is now far spent.” So he went in to stay with them.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>When he was at table with them, he took the bread and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26011AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26011AM\"></sup>blessed and broke it and gave it to them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26012AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26012AN\"></sup>And their eyes were opened, and they recognized him. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26012AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26012AO\"></sup>he vanished from their sight.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>They said to each other, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26013AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26013AP\"></sup>“Did not our hearts burn within us while he talked to us on the road, while he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26013AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26013AQ\"></sup>opened to us the Scriptures?”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And they rose that same hour and returned to Jerusalem. And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26014AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26014AR\"></sup>found the eleven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26014AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26014AS\"></sup>those who were with them gathered together,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>saying, “The Lord has risen indeed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26015AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26015AT\"></sup>has appeared to Simon!”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then they told what had happened on the road, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26016AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26016AU\"></sup>how he was known to them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26016AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26016AV\"></sup>the breaking of the bread.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>As they were talking about these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26017AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26017AW\"></sup>Jesus himself stood among them, and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Peace to you!”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26018AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26018AX\"></sup>startled and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26018AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26018AY\"></sup>frightened and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26018AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26018AZ\"></sup>thought they saw a spirit.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you troubled, and why do doubts arise in your hearts?</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>See my hands and my feet, that it is I myself. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26020BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26020BA\"></sup>Touch me, and see. For a spirit does not have flesh and bones as you see that I have.”</span>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And when he had said this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26021BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26021BB\"></sup>he showed them his hands and his feet.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And while they still disbelieved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26022BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26022BC\"></sup>for joy and were marveling, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26022BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26022BD\"></sup>he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you anything here to eat?”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They gave him a piece of broiled fish,",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>and he took it and ate before them.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26025BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26025BE\"></sup>“These are my words that I spoke to you while I was still with you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26025BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26025BF\"></sup>that everything written about me in the Law of Moses and the Prophets and the Psalms must be fulfilled.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26026BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26026BG\"></sup>he opened their minds to understand the Scriptures,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Thus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26027BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26027BH\"></sup>it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26027BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26027BI\"></sup>that the Christ should suffer and on the third day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26027BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26027BJ\"></sup>rise from the dead,</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26028BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26028BK\"></sup>repentance for the forgiveness of sins should be proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26028BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26028BL\"></sup>in his name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26028BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26028BM\"></sup>to all nations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26028BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26028BN\"></sup>beginning from Jerusalem.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26029BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26029BO\"></sup>You are witnesses of these things.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And behold, I am sending <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26030BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26030BP\"></sup>the promise of my Father upon you. But stay in the city until you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26030BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26030BQ\"></sup>are clothed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26030BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26030BR\"></sup>power <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26030BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26030BS\"></sup>from on high.”</span>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26031BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26031BT\"></sup>he led them out as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26031BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26031BU\"></sup>Bethany, and lifting up his hands he blessed them.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>While he blessed them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26032BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26032BV\"></sup>he parted from them and was carried up into heaven.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26033BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26033BW\"></sup>worshiped him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26033BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26033BX\"></sup>returned to Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26033BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26033BY\"></sup>with great joy,",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26034BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26034BZ\"></sup>were continually in the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26034CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26034CA\"></sup>blessing God."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;